Izgleda da imaju nekih
problema...

122
00:08:46,857 --> 00:08:48,222
sa bejzbol igracem.

123
00:08:48,259 --> 00:08:49,954
Prosle godine je bio klovn.

124
00:08:49,994 --> 00:08:52,462
Samo su zamenili glavu i
ofarbali ga.

125
00:08:52,496 --> 00:08:53,827
Mama mi je rekla.

126
00:08:53,864 --> 00:08:57,197
Pravi je dzin,
zar ne?

127
00:08:57,234 --> 00:09:00,067
Ne bas. Dzinovi ne postoje, 
gospodine Gailey.

128
00:09:00,104 --> 00:09:02,766
Danas mozda ne, 
Suzie...

129
00:09:02,807 --> 00:09:05,435
ali nekada,
bilo je prilicno...

130
00:09:08,345 --> 00:09:10,210
Sta je bilo sa dzinom
koga je Jack ubio?

131
00:09:10,247 --> 00:09:13,580
Jack? Koji Jack?

132
00:09:13,617 --> 00:09:14,777
Jack...

133
00:09:17,688 --> 00:09:19,588
Jack!

134
00:09:19,623 --> 00:09:21,591
"Jack and the Beanstalk."

135
00:09:21,625 --> 00:09:23,593
Nikada nisam cula za to.

136
00:09:23,627 --> 00:09:25,424
Sigurno si cula.
Samo si zaboravila.

137
00:09:25,463 --> 00:09:27,124
To je bajka.

138
00:09:27,164 --> 00:09:30,497
Oh, jedna od onih prica.
Ne znam nijednu.

139
00:09:30,534 --> 00:09:35,096
Majka i otac su ti sigurno pricali
bajke.

140
00:09:35,139 --> 00:09:37,266
Ne. Mama misli da su 
glupave.

141
00:09:37,308 --> 00:09:40,106
Ne znam da li i tata to
misli.

142
00:09:40,144 --> 00:09:41,941
Nikada ga nisam upoznala.

143
00:09:41,979 --> 00:09:45,210
Mama i tata su se razveli kada sam
bila beba.

144
00:09:49,019 --> 00:09:51,817
Pa, taj bejzbol igrac
meni lici na dzina.

145
00:09:51,856 --> 00:09:55,553
Ljudi ponekad toliko porastu,
ali to nije uobicajeno.

146
00:09:55,593 --> 00:09:58,187
Sigurno ti je i to
mama rekla.

147
00:10:06,237 --> 00:10:08,398
Zdravo.
Ja sam Suzanina mama.

148
00:10:08,439 --> 00:10:10,464
Da, znam.
Udjite...

149
00:10:10,508 --> 00:10:12,908
Suzi mi je mnogo procala o vama. 
Ja sam Fred Gailey.

150
00:10:12,943 --> 00:10:14,069
Znam.

151
00:10:14,111 --> 00:10:16,102
I meni je mnogo pricala o
vama

152
00:10:16,147 --> 00:10:19,480
- Zdravo mama!
- Zdravo draga.

153
00:10:19,517 --> 00:10:23,180
Moze kafa?
Sigurno ste se smrzli...

154
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:25,780
- Oh, ne brinite.
- Vec je gotova.

155
00:10:25,823 --> 00:10:28,724
U tpom slucaju, hvala..
Kako to se svidja moja parada??

156
00:10:28,759 --> 00:10:30,727
Bolja je nego prosle
godine.

157
00:10:30,761 --> 00:10:32,422
Nadam se da se
gospodin Macy slaze sa tobom.

158
00:10:32,463 --> 00:10:35,728
Secer? Krem?
Oba? Ni jedno?

159
00:10:35,766 --> 00:10:37,893
Jedna kocka, hvala.

160
00:10:40,437 --> 00:10:42,166
Vrlo ste ljubazni,
gospodine Gailey.

161
00:10:42,206 --> 00:10:43,468
Sedite.

162
00:10:43,507 --> 00:10:45,498
Zelim da vam zahvalim
sto ste tako dobri sa Suzan.

163
00:10:45,543 --> 00:10:48,740
Klio mi je rakao da ste ih
juce vodili u Zoo vrt.

164
00:10:48,779 --> 00:10:50,906
Jesam, ali
priznajem...

165
00:10:50,948 --> 00:10:53,678
to je deo scenarija.

166
00:10:53,717 --> 00:10:59,019
Veoma volim Suzi, ali
zeleo sam i vas da upoznam.

167
00:10:59,056 --> 00:11:01,616
Citao sam, da je najbolji nacin da
upoznas majku...

168
00:11:01,659 --> 00:11:03,388
da budes ljubazan sa
cerkom.

169
00:11:03,427 --> 00:11:05,520
Kakav strasan trik.

170
00:11:05,563 --> 00:11:07,531
Ali je dobar.

171
00:11:07,565 --> 00:11:09,692
Ide Deda Mraz.

172
00:11:09,733 --> 00:11:12,600
Ne pominji to ime.

173
00:11:12,636 --> 00:11:14,934
Mnogo je bolji nego
prosle godine.

174
00:11:14,972 --> 00:11:17,338
Ovaj bar ne nosi naocare.

175
00:11:17,374 --> 00:11:19,467
Ovaj je bio zamena, u 
poslednjem trenitku...

176
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:21,478
Onog sto sam unajmila, otpustila
sam ga

177
00:11:21,512 --> 00:11:22,809
Zasto?

178
00:11:22,847 --> 00:11:25,748
Secas se kucepazitelja od
prosle Nove Godine?

179
00:11:25,783 --> 00:11:27,978
Da.

180
00:11:28,018 --> 00:11:31,078
E, pa ovaj je bio jos gori.

181
00:11:31,121 --> 00:11:32,383
Oh.

182
00:11:32,423 --> 00:11:35,085
Vidim da ne veruje ni u
 Deda Mraza.

183
00:11:35,125 --> 00:11:37,923
Nema Deda Mraza,
ne verujem u bajke...

184
00:11:37,962 --> 00:11:41,193
ni u druge izmisljotine,
i to je to.

185
00:11:41,232 --> 00:11:43,996
Tako je. Trabalo bi
da budemo realni...

186
00:11:44,034 --> 00:11:46,002
i iskreni sa svojom
decom...

187
00:11:46,036 --> 00:11:47,503
da ne dozvolimo da odrastu
verujuci...

188
00:11:47,538 --> 00:11:51,668
u legende, mitove...
Kao sto je Deda Mraz, recimo...

189
00:11:51,709 --> 00:11:53,006
Jasno.

190
00:11:53,043 --> 00:11:56,444
To je kraj.
Akrobati su bili dobri.

191
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,505
I trebalo bi za tu cenu.

192
00:11:58,549 --> 00:12:00,346
Hvala za kafu.

193
00:12:00,384 --> 00:12:02,614
I hvala sto ste me
pozvali.

194
00:12:02,653 --> 00:12:05,053
Bilo je zadovoljstvo,
gospodjice.

195
00:12:05,089 --> 00:12:06,579
Mama, mislila sam...

196
00:12:06,624 --> 00:12:08,615
imamo tako veliku curku
za veceru..

197
00:12:08,659 --> 00:12:10,627
a samo nas je dvoje... dve...

198
00:12:10,661 --> 00:12:13,789
Mozemo li pozvati gospodina 
Gailey-a?

199
00:12:13,831 --> 00:12:15,696
Oh, nemojte...

200
00:12:15,733 --> 00:12:17,860
Pojescu vec neki
sendvic.

201
00:12:17,902 --> 00:12:19,870
Tako je velika
curka.

202
00:12:19,904 --> 00:12:21,132
Nije u tome stvar,
draga...

203
00:12:21,171 --> 00:12:23,833
sigurna sam da gospodin
Gailey ima druge planove

204
00:12:23,874 --> 00:12:26,001
Nema. Zar ne?

205
00:12:26,043 --> 00:12:29,376
Da budem iskren,
posebno sa detetom...

206
00:12:29,413 --> 00:12:31,074
Priznajem, nemam drugih
planova.

207
00:12:31,115 --> 00:12:33,310
Molim te, mama!

208
00:12:33,350 --> 00:12:34,908
Da li je u redu?

209
00:12:34,952 --> 00:12:36,146
Hmm?

210
00:12:40,958 --> 00:12:43,256
Da li je u redu,
gospodine Gailey?

211
00:12:43,294 --> 00:12:45,888
Zavisi.

212
00:12:47,564 --> 00:12:49,191
