elegantan kostim.

233
00:13:54,531 --> 00:13:58,900
Da. Imam ga
godinama.

234
00:13:58,936 --> 00:14:01,769
Bas je pravi.

235
00:14:01,805 --> 00:14:03,796
Cak je bolji i od mog.

236
00:14:03,841 --> 00:14:05,103
Je li, Alfrede?

237
00:14:05,142 --> 00:14:08,043
Glumio sam Deda Mraza
u komsiluku.

238
00:14:08,078 --> 00:14:09,204
Nemoj da pricas!

239
00:14:09,246 --> 00:14:11,214
Od pre tri godine.

240
00:14:11,248 --> 00:14:15,446
Imaju kostim, ali
ne takav...

241
00:14:15,486 --> 00:14:17,954
i od kada nosim svoj sa sobom...

242
00:14:17,988 --> 00:14:19,546
Dobio sam posao, vidis?

243
00:14:21,158 --> 00:14:23,149
Uzivas da me imitiras?

244
00:14:23,193 --> 00:14:26,185
- Da.
- Zasto?

245
00:14:26,230 --> 00:14:28,460
Ne znam. To je...

246
00:14:28,499 --> 00:14:30,865
kada dajem poklone
decici...

247
00:14:30,901 --> 00:14:33,597
volim da posmatram njihova
lica...

248
00:14:33,637 --> 00:14:35,628
i to je Bozic.

249
00:14:35,672 --> 00:14:38,505
To me cini, tako
posebnim.

250
00:14:43,013 --> 00:14:44,480
Molim!

251
00:14:44,515 --> 00:14:46,244
Kupio sam veeliku curku.

252
00:14:46,283 --> 00:14:49,548
Moja cerka je sa drugarima bila
na veceri.

253
00:14:52,656 --> 00:14:54,681
Tako znaci.

254
00:14:54,725 --> 00:14:55,851
Dobro jutro.

255
00:14:55,893 --> 00:14:58,487
Oh, kakav kostim!

256
00:14:58,529 --> 00:15:00,656
pre nego sto odes, zeleo
bih da ti dam...

257
00:15:00,697 --> 00:15:02,700
nekoliko saveta. Kako biti
dobar deda Mraz.

258
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:04,061
Hajde.

259
00:15:04,101 --> 00:15:06,934
Evo liste
igracaka.

260
00:15:06,970 --> 00:15:09,632
Igracaka kojih imamo 
previse.

261
00:15:09,673 --> 00:15:11,140
Sada, videces da vecina
dece...

262
00:15:11,175 --> 00:15:13,575
nije neodlucila, sta bi zelela
za Bozic.

263
00:15:13,610 --> 00:15:18,070
Kada se to dogodi,
predlozis jednu od ovih.

264
00:15:18,115 --> 00:15:19,241
Razumes?

265
00:15:19,283 --> 00:15:20,978
Naravno.

266
00:15:21,018 --> 00:15:23,987
Odlicno.
Zapamti ovu listu..

267
00:15:24,021 --> 00:15:25,989
Oh, ne 9:50.

268
00:15:26,023 --> 00:15:28,491
Kada zavrsis, dodji na
sedmi sprat.

269
00:15:28,525 --> 00:15:29,924
Cekacu te.

270
00:15:32,529 --> 00:15:34,292
Zamisli...

271
00:15:34,331 --> 00:15:37,198
da ucinis, da dete uzme nesto,
sto, ustvari, ne zeli...

272
00:15:37,234 --> 00:15:40,328
samo zato. sto je neko kupio mnogo, 
"pogresnih" igracaka.

273
00:15:40,370 --> 00:15:43,430
Protiv toga sam se borio,
sve ove godine...

274
00:15:43,474 --> 00:15:45,465
protiv komercijalizacije
Bozica.

275
00:15:45,509 --> 00:15:48,672
Mnogo je toga loseg
na ovom svetu...

276
00:15:48,712 --> 00:15:50,612
Jedna od najlosijih stvari - 
komercijalizacija.

277
00:15:50,647 --> 00:15:52,342
Tako je.

278
00:15:52,382 --> 00:15:54,350
Cak je i u Brooklyn-u
tako.

279
00:15:54,384 --> 00:15:56,545
Uopste ne brinu o vrednostima
Bozica.

280
00:15:56,587 --> 00:15:59,055
Samo da zarade.

281
00:15:59,089 --> 00:16:01,148
Ne brini.
Ja cu to.

282
00:16:01,191 --> 00:16:03,352
Eh?
Hvala, Alfred.

283
00:16:05,329 --> 00:16:06,728
I sta cu sa ovim?

284
00:16:06,764 --> 00:16:08,789
Baci.

285
00:16:08,832 --> 00:16:11,027
Vec mi je dosadno, da samo 
cistim prasinu.

286
00:16:11,068 --> 00:16:12,262
Mm-hmm.

287
00:16:13,504 --> 00:16:16,337
- Hvala.
- Pa, hvala, Alfred.

288
00:16:23,347 --> 00:16:26,976
Da, da, da
Peter je lepo ime.

289
00:16:27,017 --> 00:16:28,382
Sta ti zelis za Bozic,
Peter?

290
00:16:28,418 --> 00:16:31,819
Vatrogasno vozilo, kao ona velika,
samo manje...

291
00:16:31,855 --> 00:16:33,846
koje izbacuje vodu.

292
00:16:33,891 --> 00:16:36,655
Necu da prskam po kuci,
samo u dvoristu.

293
00:16:36,693 --> 00:16:38,285
Obecavam.

294
00:16:38,328 --> 00:16:39,989
Psst! Psst!

295
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:43,056
Macy ih nema.
Niko nema ta vozila.

296
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:45,660
Pa, Peter,
Ti si dobar decko.

297
00:16:45,702 --> 00:16:46,930
Dobices vatrogasno
vozilo.

298
00:16:46,970 --> 00:16:49,837
Oh, hvala puno!

299
00:16:49,873 --> 00:16:53,104
Vidis? Rekao sam da
ce mi dati.

300
00:16:53,143 --> 00:16:55,111
Divno.
To je stvarno lepo.

301
00:16:55,145 --> 00:16:56,669
Sacekaj ovde.

302
00:16:56,713 --> 00:17:00,149
I mama hoce da se zahvali
Deda Mrazu.

303
00:17:00,184 --> 00:17:02,618
Kazi, sta je sa tobom?

304
00:17:02,653 --> 00:17:04,143
Ne razumes kada ti govorim?

305
00:17:04,188 --> 00:17:07,180
Kazem: niko nema
ta vozila.

306
00:17:07,224 --> 00:17:09,522
Stojim ovde satima. Noge
me bole.

307
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:11,528
Jaka stvar, obecati detetu.

308
00:17:11,562 --> 00:17:14,895
Mislis da obecavan nesto u sta
nisam siguran?

309
00:17:14,932 --> 00:17:18,732
Mozes da pronadjes to vozilo u
Schoenfeld's u Lexington-u.

310
00:17:18,769 --> 00:17:20,703
Samo 8.50. 
Veoma povoljno.

311
00:17:20,737 --> 00:17:23,103
Schoenfeld's?
Ne razumem.

312
00:17:23,140 --> 00:17:25,973
Pratim sta se dogadja na
trzistu igracaka..

313
00:17:26,009 --> 00:17:27,340
To te iznenadjuje?

314
00:17:27,377 --> 00:17:28,969
Iznenadjuje?

315
00:17:29,012 --> 00:17:31,503
Macy salje ljude u
druge robne kuce?

316
00:17:31,548 --> 00:17:32,845
Salis se?

317
00:17:32,883 --> 00:17:35,818
Najvaznije je da dete
bude srecno.

318
00:17:35,853 --> 00:17:38,913
Ko prodaje igracke, nije
uopste vazno.

319
00:17:38,956 --> 00:17:40,514
Zar ne mislis tako?

320
00:17:40,557 --> 00:17:43,025
Ko, ja? Naravno.

321
00:17:43,060 --> 00:17:44,789
Ne verujem da i Macy
tako misli.

322
00:17:44,828 --> 00:17:46,591
Dokle god sam ja ovde,
tako misle.

323
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:48,495
Ne razumem.

324
00:17:48,532 --> 00:17:52,059
Stvarno, ne razumem.

325
00:18:12,823 --> 00:18:14,290
Razumem, razumem.

326
00:18:14,324 --> 00:18:16,121
Ti bi malena, zelela
slicuge.

327
00:18:16,159 --> 00:18:17,751
Ali, naravno, one
najbolje..

328
00:18:17,794 --> 00:18:20,194
Koje ce zastititi njene
male clanke.

329
00:18:20,230 --> 00:18:23,597
Nase slicuge su dobre, ali ne
i najbolje..

330
00:18:23,634 --> 00:18:25,659
Idi u Gimbels.

331
00:18:25,702 --> 00:18:27,226
Oni imaju ono sto
ti je potrebno.

332
00:18:27,271 --> 00:18:29,637
Izvoli, draga. To je
za tebe.

333
00:18:29,673 --> 00:18:30,799
Srecan Bozic.

334
00:18:30,841 --> 00:18:32,001
Gimbels.

335
00:18:32,042 --> 00:18:35,705
Zdravo, malena.
Koliko imas godina?

336
00:18:37,881 --> 00:18:40,111
Gimbels.

337
00:18:40,150 --> 00:18:42,311
Gimbels!

338
00:18:42,352 --> 00:18:44,183
Izvinite. Cuvar je rekao
da se vama obratim.

339
00:18:44,221 --> 00:18:45,688
Vi ste glavni u odeljenju
igracaka?

340
00:18:45,722 --> 00:18:47,189
Da, gospodjo...

341
00:18:47,224 --> 00:18:49,920
Slusajte. Cestitam vama i
gospodinu  Macy-ju...

342
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:52,485
na ovom novom osoblju.

343
00:18:52,529 --> 00:18:55,123
Zamislite, poslati ljude u 
druge prodavnice.

344
00:18:55,165 --> 00:18:56,826
Ne razumem Zasto? 
Da li je...

345
00:18:56,867 --> 00:18:59,427
- Naravno.
- Vi ste to rekli.

346
00:18:59,469 --> 00:19:01,596
Zamislite, velika robna kuca
kao sto je Macy's...

347
00:19:01,638 --> 00:19:04,163
duh Bozica, stavlja
ispred sopstvene zarade.

348
00:19:04,207 --> 00:19:06,004
To je prelepo.

349
00:19:06,043 --> 00:19:08,102
Nikada nisam ovde mnogo
kupovala...

350
00:19:08,145 --> 00:19:12,343
ali od sada, bicu redovna 
musterija u Macy-ju.

351
00:19:12,382 --> 00:19:13,781
U redu, draga.

352
00:19:13,817 --> 00:19:15,444
Hvala vam gospodjo.

353
00:19:18,855 --> 00:19:21,756
Ima jos sest zena koje bi
da vam se zahvale

354
00:19:21,792 --> 00:19:25,057
Ne sada. Moram o ovome da 
razmislim.

355
00:19:25,095 --> 00:19:28,223
Licno, mislim da je to 
divna ideja.

356
00:19:28,265 --> 00:19:31,132
Vi tako mislite.
Te zene misle isto.

357
00:19:31,168 --> 00:19:34,103
Pitanje je, da li
ce i gospodin Macy tako misliti?

358
00:19:37,341 --> 00:19:40,469
Izgleda prilicno blesavo,
gospodine Gailey.

359
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:43,274
Mislio sam, kada smo 
vec u radnji..

360
00:19:43,313 --> 00:19:45,474
mozemo da pozdravimo
Deda Mraza.

361
00:19:45,515 --> 00:19:46,982
Zasto?

362
00:19:47,017 --> 00:19:49,144
Zato sto kada budes 
razgovarala sa njim...

363
00:19:49,186 --> 00:19:51,279
mozda ces i promeniti
misljenje o njemu.

364
00:19:56,860 --> 00:19:59,829
Do vidjenja, Elmer.
Budi dobar decko.

365
00:19:59,863 --> 00:20:01,125
Srecan Bozic!

366
00:20:02,199 --> 00:20:03,689
Pa, mlada damo, kako
ti je ime?

367
00:20:03,734 --> 00:20:05,895
Susan Walker.
A tvoje?

368
00:20:05,936 --> 00:20:08,131
Moje? Kris Kringle.

369
00:20:08,171 --> 00:20:10,139
Ja sam Deda Mraz.

370
00:20:10,173 --> 00:20:13,506
Oh, ti u to ne verujes
zar ne?

371
00:20:13,543 --> 00:20:17,604
Moja mama je gospodja Walker,
koja te je zaposlila.

372
00:20:17,647 --> 00:20:19,114
Oh.

373
00:20:19,149 --> 00:20:22,209
Moram reci, najbolji
si od svih.

374
00:20:22,252 --> 00:20:23,514
Stvarno?

375
00:20:23,553 --> 00:20:26,113
Tvoja brada ne doseze do usiju....

376
00:20:26,156 --> 00:20:29,319
Zato sto je prava. Ja sam stvarno
Deda Mraz.

377
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:32,528
Hajde, hajde, nastavi...

378
00:20:33,830 --> 00:20:35,161
Ups...

379
00:20:37,901 --> 00:20:39,835
Dobro je, narode,
ne gurajte se.

380
00:20:39,870 --> 00:20:41,531
Imate ceo dan da vidite
Deda Mraza.

381
00:20:41,571 --> 00:20:43,937
Polako, deco..
Ovuda, molim.

382
00:20:43,974 --> 00:20:45,373
Vratite se u red.

383
00:20:45,409 --> 00:20:48,435
Sta bi zelela da ti donesem
za Bozic?

384
00:20:48,478 --> 00:20:50,378
Nista, hvala.

385
00:20:50,414 --> 00:20:52,609
Nemoj tako.
Sigurno zelis nesto.

386
00:20:52,649 --> 00:20:54,981
Sta god da je,
mama ce mi dati...

387
00:20:55,018 --> 00:20:57,486
ako je razumno,
i ne kosta mnogo.

388
00:20:57,521 --> 00:20:58,647
Zdravo, mama.

389
00:20:58,688 --> 00:21:00,121
Zdravo, Suzan, 
gospodine Gailey.

390
00:21:00,157 --> 00:21:03,490
Mislim da si ovom gospodinu,
oduzela dovoljno vremena.

391
00:21:03,527 --> 00:21:06,826
Objasnjenje je jednostavno.

392
00:21:06,863 --> 00:21:08,490
Kleova mama je povredila
clanak.

393
00:21:08,532 --> 00:21:11,000
I zamolila me je da dovedem Suzi.

394
00:21:11,034 --> 00:21:13,525
Da. Kleo me je zvala.
Bas sam se pitala, gde ste.

395
00:21:13,570 --> 00:21:16,232
Morali smo da se javimo
Deda Mrazu.

396
00:21:16,273 --> 00:21:19,970
On je divni stari gospodin,
i brada mu je prava.

397
00:21:20,010 --> 00:21:22,979
Da, draga. Mnogi muskarci
imaju takvu bradu.

398
00:21:23,013 --> 00:21:24,844
Suzan, stani ovde 
za cas.

399
00:21:24,881 --> 00:21:27,349
Zelim da razgovaram sa
gospodinom Gailey-em.

400
00:21:27,384 --> 00:21:30,353
Nije trebalo da dovedem Suzi, da
vidi Deda Mraza?

401
00:21:30,387 --> 00:21:33,322
Pored vas se osecam kao losa majka.

402
00:21:33,356 --> 00:21:35,517
Zao mi je, ali mislio sam nista lose
u tome

403
00:21:35,559 --> 00:21:37,459
da se pozdravi sa starim.

404
00:21:37,494 --> 00:21:39,359
Ja mislim da je lose.

405
00:21:39,396 --> 00:21:41,990
Rekla sam joj da je Deda Mraz
mit, a vi ste je doveli...

406
00:21:42,032 --> 00:21:44,159
ovde medju hiljadu zavedene
dece...

407
00:21:44,201 --> 00:21:47,102
koja se susrecu sa starcem, cija je
brada prava.

408
00:21:47,137 --> 00:21:50,368
To ce je vrlo zbuniti...

409
00:21:50,407 --> 00:21:53,069
Sta ce pomisliti?
Kome ce verovati?

410
00:21:58,715 --> 00:22:00,205
I pricati im sve te bajke...

411
00:22:00,250 --> 00:22:03,651
Odrastaju misleci da je zivot 
fantazija.

412
00:22:03,687 --> 00:22:06,656
Cekace ceo zivot na princa...

413
00:22:06,690 --> 00:22:08,658
a kada i nadje, na kraju
ispadne...

414
00:22:08,692 --> 00:22:11,490
Pricamo o Suzi, ne o
vama.

415
00:22:11,528 --> 00:22:13,325
Bez obzira, da li se
slazete, ili ne...

416
00:22:13,363 --> 00:22:16,594
Molim vas da postujete moje 
vaspitanje Suzi.

417
00:22:16,633 --> 00:22:18,430
Ona je moja odgovornost...

418
00:22:18,468 --> 00:22:20,333
I ja je moram osposobiti
za zivot.

419
00:22:20,370 --> 00:22:21,530
U redu.

420
00:22:29,346 --> 00:22:31,337
- Reci "Hvala"
- Hvala.

421
00:22:31,381 --> 00:22:33,076
Dovidjenja. Srecan Bozic!

422
00:22:35,652 --> 00:22:37,779
I, mlada damo, kako ti je
ime?

423
00:22:37,821 --> 00:22:39,914
Zao mi je, ona ne zna
Engleski jezik.

424
00:22:39,956 --> 00:22:42,754
Ona je Holandjanka. 
Tak je stigla.

425
00:22:42,792 --> 00:22:44,851
Ona je usvojeno dete...

426
00:22:44,894 --> 00:22:47,522
iz Rotterdama je...

427
00:22:47,564 --> 00:22:48,792
Mi smo je usvojili.

428
00:22:48,832 --> 00:22:51,323
Rekli smo joj da je necete 
razumeti...

429
00:22:51,368 --> 00:22:53,336
ali, kada vas je juce ugledala 
na paradi...

430
00:22:53,370 --> 00:22:55,998
rekla je da ste
"Sinter Claes"...

431
00:22:56,039 --> 00:22:57,973
i da cete je razumeti.

432
00:22:58,008 --> 00:22:59,134
Nisam znala sta da
radim.

433
00:22:59,175 --> 00:23:02,144
Zdravo.

434
00:23:48,391 --> 00:23:50,018
Razumes me?

435
00:23:50,060 --> 00:23:51,857
Da, znam sta mislis, mama.

436
00:23:51,895 --> 00:23:53,123
Dobro.

437
00:23:53,163 --> 00:23:56,564
Ali kada je razgovarao na
holandskom sa devojcicom...

438
00:23:56,599 --> 00:24:00,057
Suzan, ja znam francuski,
ali nisam Jovanka Orleanka.

439
00:24:00,103 --> 00:24:03,072
Ali , hocu da kazem da..
Slobodno...

440
00:24:03,106 --> 00:24:04,937
Zeleli ste da me vidite
gospodjo Walker.

441
00:24:04,974 --> 00:24:06,441
Udjite.

442
00:24:06,476 --> 00:24:08,034
Zdravo! Lepo je 
ponovo te videti.

443
00:24:08,078 --> 00:24:09,443
Drago mi je da te vidim.

444
00:24:09,479 --> 00:24:10,878
Bas ste srecni,
gospodjo Walker.

445
00:24:10,914 --> 00:24:12,643
Imate divnu devojcicu.

446
00:24:12,682 --> 00:24:15,617
Hvala. Zvala sam vas zato sto...

447
00:24:15,652 --> 00:24:16,949
je Suzan prilicno
zbunjena...

448
00:24:16,986 --> 00:24:18,510
i mislila sam da cete nam 
pomoci.

449
00:24:18,555 --> 00:24:19,817
Rado.

450
00:24:19,856 --> 00:24:23,690
Recite joj, molim vas, da vi
niste Deda Mraz...

451
00:24:23,727 --> 00:24:26,355
i da on ustvari ne postoji.

452
00:24:26,396 --> 00:24:28,330
Zao mi je, sto se necu sloziti
sa vama, gospodjo Walker.

453
00:24:28,364 --> 00:24:31,197
Ne samo da postoji, nego cu joj to
i dokazati.

454
00:24:31,234 --> 00:24:33,293
Ne, ne razumete.

455
00:24:33,336 --> 00:24:36,305
Zelim da joj kazete istinu.
Kako se zovete?

456
00:24:36,339 --> 00:24:38,364
Kris Kringle. Kladim se, da si
u prvom razredu.

457
00:24:38,408 --> 00:24:39,534
U drugom.

458
00:24:39,576 --> 00:24:41,203
Mislim, vase pravo ime.

459
00:24:41,244 --> 00:24:43,508
To je moje pravo ime.
Drugi razred?

460
00:24:43,546 --> 00:24:44,945
Da. U skoli za
 nadarene.

461
00:24:44,981 --> 00:24:47,643
Oh, za
nadarene.

462
00:24:47,684 --> 00:24:50,084
Mogu li dopiti podatke 
zaposlenog?

463
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:51,246
Da, gospodjo Walker.

464
00:24:51,287 --> 00:24:52,720
Lepa ti je haljina.

465
00:24:52,756 --> 00:24:54,621
Gde si li je samo
kupila?

466
00:24:54,657 --> 00:24:57,387
Ovde u Macy-ju.
Imamo 10% popusta.

467
00:24:57,427 --> 00:25:00,396
Molim vas, ne morate da se
pretvarate zbog Suzan.

468
00:25:00,430 --> 00:25:02,364
Ona je vrlo inteligentno
dete...

469
00:25:02,398 --> 00:25:04,491
i uvek zeli da sazna pravu
istinu.

470
00:25:04,534 --> 00:25:06,434
Dobro je. Ja joj uvek i govorim
pravu istinu.

471
00:25:06,469 --> 00:25:09,461
Tvoja skola... kako ti
se zove uciteljica?

472
00:25:09,506 --> 00:25:11,599
Gospodja Haley.

473
00:25:11,641 --> 00:25:14,235
- Izvolite gospodjo Walker.
- Hvala.

474
00:25:14,277 --> 00:25:16,643
Sta radis jos, sem
citanja i igranja?

475
00:25:16,679 --> 00:25:19,842
Imamo i odmore po 
pola sata.

476
00:25:19,883 --> 00:25:21,976
Ali nije sve u tome, zar ne?

477
00:25:22,018 --> 00:25:25,146
Ne. Nije nam dozvoljeno da 
caskamo, i tako....

478
00:25:25,188 --> 00:25:28,624
U utorak, Chester Richards
je pricao sve vreme.

479
00:25:28,658 --> 00:25:30,717
To je bas bilo lose?

480
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:34,287
Gospodja Haley ga je poslala na 
odmor samog, skoro citav sat.

481
00:25:34,330 --> 00:25:38,494
Suzan, izadji do
gospodjice Adams?

482
00:25:38,535 --> 00:25:40,162
Odmah cu doci.

483
00:25:40,203 --> 00:25:41,670
U redu. Zdravo.

484
00:25:41,704 --> 00:25:43,501
Zdravo, mlada damo. Nadam
se da cemo se opet videti.

485
00:25:43,540 --> 00:25:45,838
Hvala. I ja se
nadam. Zdravo.
.

486
00:25:45,875 --> 00:25:47,001
Zdravo.

487
00:25:47,043 --> 00:25:50,501
Zao mi je, gospodine., uh... 
gospodine ...

488
00:25:50,547 --> 00:25:51,844
Kringle.

489
00:25:51,881 --> 00:25:53,849
Zao mi je, ali moracemo, nesto
da promenimo.

490
00:25:53,883 --> 00:25:55,009
Da promenimo?

491
00:25:55,051 --> 00:25:57,178
Deda Mraz koga smo imali, pre
dve godine...

492
00:25:57,220 --> 00:25:59,347
se vratio,
mislim da mu dugujemo...

493
00:25:59,389 --> 00:26:00,856
Da li sam nesto pogresio?

494
00:26:00,890 --> 00:26:02,949
Oh, ne, ne.

495
00:26:02,992 --> 00:26:04,619
Onda...

496
00:26:06,262 --> 00:26:07,388
Da?

497
00:26:07,430 --> 00:26:09,955
Gospodin Macy zeli da vas
vidi, odmah.

498
00:26:09,999 --> 00:26:11,489
Dolazim.

499
00:26:13,503 --> 00:26:15,164
Mozete li da sednete...

500
00:26:15,205 --> 00:26:18,299
i odmah se vracam sa 
cekom od vase plate.

501
00:26:20,009 --> 00:26:21,476
Da, zaista.

502
00:26:21,511 --> 00:26:25,038
Udjite.
Gospodin Macy vas ocekuje.

503
00:26:26,549 --> 00:26:29,017
Utisak koji ce ostaviti 
na javnost...

504
00:26:29,052 --> 00:26:30,451
Oh, udjite,
gospodjo Walker.

505
00:26:30,486 --> 00:26:34,286
- Dobar dan gospodjo Walker.
- Sedite.

506
00:26:34,324 --> 00:26:37,452
Pricao sam ovoj gospodi o 
novoj politici poslovanja...

507
00:26:37,493 --> 00:26:39,154
koju ste vi i gospodin
Shellhammer zapoceli.

508
00:26:39,195 --> 00:26:41,959
ne mogu reci da odobravam...
sasvim..

509
00:26:41,998 --> 00:26:43,863
odeljenje reklame,
je vise nego zadovoljno...

510
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:47,301
ali ovakav odziv potrosaca...

511
00:26:47,337 --> 00:26:49,305
Prosto, ne mogu biti
ljut na vas.

512
00:26:49,339 --> 00:26:51,671
- O cemu govori?
- Reci cu ti kasnije.

513
00:26:51,708 --> 00:26:53,073
Da nastavim, gospodo...

514
00:26:53,109 --> 00:26:56,875
Priznajem, ovaj plan zvuci
blesavo i nemoguce.

515
00:26:56,913 --> 00:27:00,576
Zamislite Macy-ev Deda Mraz
salje kupce u Gimbels.

516
00:27:00,617 --> 00:27:05,213
Ho ho. Ali, gospodo,
ne mozete sporiti uspeh.

517
00:27:05,255 --> 00:27:07,246
Pogledajte.

518
00:27:07,290 --> 00:27:09,258
Telegrami,
poruke, pozivi.

519
00:27:09,292 --> 00:27:11,283
Guvernerova zena,
gradonacelnikova zena...

520
00:27:11,327 --> 00:27:13,295
preko 500 zadovoljnih
roditelja...

521
00:27:13,329 --> 00:27:15,559
izrazavaju nedvosmislenu
zahvalnost Macy-ju.

522
00:27:15,598 --> 00:27:18,032
Nikada se to nije dogodilo
u mojoj karijeri..

523
00:27:18,067 --> 00:27:20,433
toliko iskrenih i ekspresnih
odgovora...

524
00:27:20,470 --> 00:27:22,199
nasoj politici
poslovanja.

525
00:27:22,238 --> 00:27:25,935
Da li sam u pravu, Frank,
ako nastavimo ovako...

526
00:27:25,975 --> 00:27:27,943
imacemo sve bolje
rezultate.

527
00:27:27,977 --> 00:27:30,502
I vise od toga. 
Od sada...

528
00:27:30,546 --> 00:27:32,946
ne samo da ce nas Deda Mraz 
nastaviti po svome...

529
00:27:32,982 --> 00:27:35,712
nego zelim i da svaki
prodavac...

530
00:27:35,752 --> 00:27:37,549
cini upravo isto.

531
00:27:37,587 --> 00:27:40,457
Ukoliko nemamo ono
sto kupac zeli...

532
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:42,649
poslacemo ga tamo gde moze
to da nabavi.

533
00:27:42,692 --> 00:27:44,660
Nema vise pritiska na kupce...

534
00:27:44,694 --> 00:27:46,321
da kupe ono, sto ne zele

535
00:27:46,362 --> 00:27:49,695
Bicemo poznati kao prodavnica
 koja pomaze...

536
00:27:49,732 --> 00:27:52,394
kao prijatelji,
robna kuca sa srcem...

537
00:27:52,435 --> 00:27:56,098
kuca kojoj je usluga kupca
ispred profita.

538
00:27:56,139 --> 00:27:59,108
I, najzad, imacemo veci profit
nego ikada pre.

539
00:27:59,142 --> 00:28:01,978
Da, znam da je kasno,
i da smo umorni...

540
00:28:02,013 --> 00:28:03,377
i da zelimo na veceru..

541
00:28:03,413 --> 00:28:05,643
i zato nastavljamo odmah
ujutru.

542
00:28:05,682 --> 00:28:07,912
U medjuvremenu,
drzite se zajedno...

543
00:28:07,951 --> 00:28:10,112
i smislite kako da promovisemo
ovo, na najbolji nacin.

544
00:28:10,153 --> 00:28:12,348
Mi mozemo to. Laku noc, R.H.

545
00:28:12,388 --> 00:28:13,514
Laku noc.

546
00:28:13,556 --> 00:28:16,753
Zelim oboma da vam zahvalim,
ponovo.

547
00:28:16,793 --> 00:28:18,454
Kao i u vasim bozicnim
kovertama...

548
00:28:18,495 --> 00:28:21,157
na najprakticnijem mogucem 
nacinu zahvalnosti.

549
00:28:21,197 --> 00:28:22,323
Hvala, gospodine Macy.

550
00:28:22,365 --> 00:28:24,356
Recite tom Deki, da necu ni 
njega zaboraviti.

551
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:26,300
Da, gospodine Macy.

552
00:28:29,906 --> 00:28:32,602
Zamislite bonus!

553
00:28:32,642 --> 00:28:35,873
Pomislio je da je to nasa ideja.
Sta je bilo?

554
00:28:35,912 --> 00:28:37,903
- Otpustila sam ga.
- Koga?

555
00:28:37,947 --> 00:28:40,177
- Deda Mraza.
- Sta?

556
00:28:40,216 --> 00:28:42,377
On je lud.
On misli da je Deda Mraz.

557
00:28:42,418 --> 00:28:44,648
Nije me briga i da misli da
je Uskrsnji zeka.

558
00:28:44,687 --> 00:28:45,881
Vrati ga.

559
00:28:45,922 --> 00:28:47,412
On je lud,
kazem ti.

560
00:28:47,457 --> 00:28:49,891
Zaposlicemo nekog drugog.

561
00:28:49,926 --> 00:28:52,451
Cula si gospodina Macy-ja.
Moramo ga zadrzati.

562
00:28:52,495 --> 00:28:54,656
A sta ako je sprecen?

563
00:28:54,697 --> 00:28:56,892
Oo, ne
Moramo reci gospodinu Macy-ju.

564
00:28:56,933 --> 00:28:59,401
Mozda je ipak, samo malo
lud...

565
00:28:59,435 --> 00:29:01,403
kao, recimo, slikari, ili
kompozitori..

566
00:29:01,437 --> 00:29:03,337
ili neki od "onih" ljudi u
Vasingtonu.

567
00:29:03,373 --> 00:29:05,307
Ne mozemo biti sigurni,
dok ga ne pregledaju.

568
00:29:05,341 --> 00:29:08,708
Ako ga otpustis, i saznamo
da ustvari nije lud...

569
00:29:08,745 --> 00:29:12,112
Gospodin Macy ce otpustiti nas.

570
00:29:12,148 --> 00:29:14,446
Moramo biti sigurni.

571
00:29:14,484 --> 00:29:16,349
I mozemo, ako gospodin Sawyer
razgovara sa njim.

572
00:29:16,386 --> 00:29:18,115
Naravno.
On je psiholog.

573
00:29:18,154 --> 00:29:20,588
On je placen da pregleda
zaposlene.

574
00:29:20,623 --> 00:29:23,421
Dok ne dobijemo njegov izvestaj,
necemo nista reci

575
00:29:23,459 --> 00:29:25,859
Odmah cu ga pozvati.

576
00:29:25,895 --> 00:29:27,692
Ali, prvo,
Vrati tog deda Mraza!

577
00:29:27,730 --> 00:29:30,096
Pregled je besmislen,
bez pacijenta.

578
00:29:31,434 --> 00:29:34,130
Samo zato, sto sam mislila
da mu dugujemo...

579
00:29:34,170 --> 00:29:36,730
ali gospodin Macy je predlozio da 
nadjemo nesto drugo...

580
00:29:36,773 --> 00:29:39,901
za njega, i
zadrzimo vas.

581
00:29:39,943 --> 00:29:43,003
Oh, pa, hvala.
To je dobra vest.

582
00:29:43,046 --> 00:29:45,446
Bicete onda ovde,
ujutru?

583
00:29:45,481 --> 00:29:46,607
Naravno, da hocu.

584
00:29:46,649 --> 00:29:49,447
Gospodjo Walker, ovo je prava
prilika za mene.

585
00:29:49,485 --> 00:29:51,419
Vise od 50 godina..

586
00:29:51,454 --> 00:29:53,649
Sve sam vise zabrinut,
zbog Bozica.

587
00:29:53,690 --> 00:29:57,387
Svi smo veoma zauzeti da
pobedimo onog drugog...

588
00:29:57,427 --> 00:30:00,419
to sve ubrzava,
izgleda bolje, i manje kosta...

589
00:30:00,463 --> 00:30:03,660
Bozic i ja, kao da smo se 
negde izgubili.

590
00:30:03,700 --> 00:30:06,498
Nije bas tako.
Bozic je, ipak, Bozic.

591
00:30:06,536 --> 00:30:08,663
Bozic nije samo dan.

592
00:30:08,705 --> 00:30:11,731
To je osecaj, misao..
To je ono sto se promenilo.

593
00:30:11,774 --> 00:30:14,937
Zato mi je drago da sam ovde.
Mozda nesto mogu da ucinim.

594
00:30:14,978 --> 00:30:16,673
I drago mi je da sa upoznao vas
i vasu cerku.

595
00:30:16,713 --> 00:30:18,738
Vi ste za mene pravi izazov.

596
00:30:18,781 --> 00:30:20,078
Mi?

597
00:30:20,116 --> 00:30:22,676
Da. Vi ste sve to "u malom".

598
00:30:22,719 --> 00:30:25,688
Ako uspem sa vama, onda sam
uspeo.

599
00:30:25,722 --> 00:30:29,488
Ako ne,
onda sam gotov.

600
00:30:29,525 --> 00:30:32,722
Ali, upozoravam vas,
ne odustajem tako lako.

601
00:30:32,762 --> 00:30:34,252
Laku noc.

602
00:30:34,297 --> 00:30:35,423
Laku noc.

603
00:30:35,465 --> 00:30:37,797
Oh, gospodine Kringle,
ujutru javite se prvo...

604
00:30:37,834 --> 00:30:40,098
gospodinu Sawyer-u?

605
00:30:40,136 --> 00:30:42,900
On ce vas "malo" pregledati.

606
00:30:42,939 --> 00:30:45,703
Oh, to vazi za sve
zaposlene.

607
00:30:45,742 --> 00:30:47,539
Pregled mentalnog zdravlja?

608
00:30:48,745 --> 00:30:50,770
Pa..

609
00:30:50,813 --> 00:30:53,509
Nema problema.
Imao sam ih onoliko.

610
00:30:53,549 --> 00:30:56,609
Ni na jednom nisam pao.
Znam ih napamet.

611
00:30:56,653 --> 00:31:00,350
- Koliko je dana u nedelji?
- Sedam.

612
00:31:00,390 --> 00:31:02,950
- Koliko prstiju vidite?
- Cetiri.

613
00:31:02,992 --> 00:31:04,983
Koordinacija misica.

614
00:31:09,399 --> 00:31:11,162
Nema ostecenja vaseg 
nervnog sistema.

615
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:13,600
Ko je bio prvi predsednik US?

616
00:31:13,636 --> 00:31:14,967
George Washington.

617
00:31:15,004 --> 00:31:18,269
Ko je bio premijer za vreme
 John Quincy Adams-a?

618
00:31:19,275 --> 00:31:21,607
Daniel D. Tompkins.

619
00:31:21,644 --> 00:31:23,976
Kladim se da vas gospodin
 Sawyer to i ne zna.

620
00:31:24,013 --> 00:31:25,173
Laku noc.

621
00:31:38,294 --> 00:31:40,228
Gospodjice Adams, da li mozete
da me spojite sa...

622
00:31:40,263 --> 00:31:43,494
the Brooks' Memorial Home
in Great Neck?

623
00:31:43,533 --> 00:31:46,161
to je staracki dom.
Tako je.

624
00:31:46,202 --> 00:31:48,693
zelim da razgovaram
sa glavnim doktorom.

625
00:31:57,380 --> 00:32:00,008
- Koliko je dana u nedelji?
- Sedam.

626
00:32:00,049 --> 00:32:02,574
Prvi predsednik US?

627
00:32:02,618 --> 00:32:03,744
George Washington.

628
00:32:03,786 --> 00:32:05,083
Tri puta pet?

629
00:32:05,121 --> 00:32:07,749
Vec ste me pitali.
Odgovor je...

630
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:09,951
Ja vodim ovaj pregled.

631
00:32:09,992 --> 00:32:11,789
Koliko je tri puta
pet?

632
00:32:11,828 --> 00:32:14,695
Kao i ranije... 15.

633
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:20,928
Prilicno ste nervozni,
zar ne, gospodine Sawyer?

634
00:32:20,970 --> 00:32:22,631
Da li ste dovoljno spavali?

635
00:32:22,672 --> 00:32:24,663
Moje navike nisu vasa stvar.

636
00:32:24,707 --> 00:32:27,835
Oh, izvinite. Ne
volim kada je nesto zapetljano...

637
00:32:27,877 --> 00:32:30,505
- Koliko prstiju vidite?
- Tri.

638
00:32:30,546 --> 00:32:33,037
I grizete nokte.
Tsssss.

639
00:32:33,082 --> 00:32:36,415
Zelim da stanete sa
skupljenim nogama......

640
00:32:36,452 --> 00:32:38,477
i rukama...
I zelim da...

641
00:32:38,521 --> 00:32:39,988
Test koordinacije misisca?

642
00:32:40,022 --> 00:32:43,389
Naravno. Vrlo rado, Ha, ha.

643
00:32:45,695 --> 00:32:49,153
Ponekad je uzrok nervih 
ostecenja, kao kod vas...

644
00:32:49,198 --> 00:32:51,496
tako ocigledan. Ne.

645
00:32:51,534 --> 00:32:54,401
ponekad je to zbog nesigurnosti.

646
00:32:54,437 --> 00:32:56,064
Jeste li srecni kod kuce?

647
00:32:56,105 --> 00:32:57,538
To je sve!

648
00:32:57,573 --> 00:32:59,768
Pregled je zavrsen.
Mozete ici.

649
00:32:59,809 --> 00:33:00,935
Hvala.

650
00:33:00,977 --> 00:33:02,308
Idite odmah.

651
00:33:05,481 --> 00:33:07,472
I ako vas zanima...

652
00:33:07,517 --> 00:33:09,849
ja sam srecno ozenjen vec
26 godina.

653
00:33:09,886 --> 00:33:12,946
Stvarno? Drago mi je
da to cujem.

654
00:33:12,989 --> 00:33:14,354
Dovidjenja.

655
00:33:18,995 --> 00:33:20,121
Dajte mi gospodju Walker.

656
00:33:20,163 --> 00:33:22,893
Da, gospodine. Vasa supriga
je na 672.

657
00:33:22,932 --> 00:33:24,729
Kaze da je vazno.

658
00:33:26,569 --> 00:33:30,471
Koliko puta sam ti rekao da me
ne uznemiravas u kancelariji?

659
00:33:30,506 --> 00:33:33,475
Ne. Ni peni.
Dao sam ti svu slobodu...

660
00:33:33,509 --> 00:33:35,170
I sama se staraj o kuci.

661
00:33:35,211 --> 00:33:37,179
Kada bi tvoj glupi brat
nasao posao...

662
00:33:37,213 --> 00:33:39,374
ne bi mene vise maltretirala.

663
00:33:41,918 --> 00:33:45,354
Gospodjo Walker, zeleo bih da 
popricamo o Kringle-u.

664
00:33:45,388 --> 00:33:48,482
Ooo, da. Dr. Pierce
iz Brooks-ove kuce je ovde.

665
00:33:48,524 --> 00:33:50,389
Pravo je vreme da razjasnimo
neke stvari.

666
00:33:50,426 --> 00:33:52,485
Izvinite, doktore, to je
bio gospodin Sawyer...

667
00:33:52,528 --> 00:33:54,519
gospodin o kome sam
vam pricala.

668
00:33:54,564 --> 00:33:56,725
On je tu na spratu.

669
00:33:56,766 --> 00:34:00,258
Cenimo vase vreme.

670
00:34:00,303 --> 00:34:03,500
U stvari,
hteo sam da vas zovem.

671
00:34:03,539 --> 00:34:07,305
Cini se da se zanimate za Krisa.

672
00:34:07,343 --> 00:34:10,278
Dr. Pierce, gospodin Sawyer.

673
00:34:10,313 --> 00:34:11,610
Kako ste?

674
00:34:11,647 --> 00:34:14,445
Nakon sto sam detaljno pregledao
onog coveka...

675
00:34:14,483 --> 00:34:16,508
moje misljenje je da bi ga
trebalo sto pre odstraniti.

676
00:34:16,552 --> 00:34:19,919
Stvarno? Nije prosao pregled?

677
00:34:19,956 --> 00:34:22,447
- Da.
- Nije odgovarao tacno?

678
00:34:22,491 --> 00:34:25,460
Jeste, ali nije
bio koncentrisan.

679
00:34:25,494 --> 00:34:27,962
Stalno je menjao teme.
Cak me i ispitivao.

680
00:34:27,997 --> 00:34:29,965
Nema sunmnje u to.

681
00:34:29,999 --> 00:34:31,967
Trebalo bi ga smestiti u
neku ustanovu.

682
00:34:32,001 --> 00:34:34,993
Ne slazem se.
Ljude smestaju...

683
00:34:35,037 --> 00:34:37,174
da ne bi povredili sebe
ili druge.

684
00:34:37,307 --> 00:34:39,172
Gospodine Kringle
on nije sposoban ni za jedno.

685
00:34:39,209 --> 00:34:40,676
On je samo "dobar".

686
00:34:40,710 --> 00:34:42,644
On je samo prijateljski na-
strojen, i zeli da bude od pomoci.

687
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:44,544
Tako se i meni cini.

688
00:34:44,581 --> 00:34:46,674
Hiljade ljudi ima ista 
predubedjenja...

689
00:34:46,716 --> 00:34:48,650
i zive savreno "normalne' zivote.

690
00:34:48,685 --> 00:34:51,552
Najpoznatiji primer je 
taj momak...

691
00:34:51,588 --> 00:34:54,056
ne mogu da se setim imena...

692
00:34:54,090 --> 00:34:56,490
Godinama misli da je
Ruski princ.

693
00:34:56,526 --> 00:34:58,551
Ima mnogo dokaza protiv
toga...

694
00:34:58,595 --> 00:35:00,495
ali nista strasno.

695
00:35:00,530 --> 00:35:01,997
Da li je u nekoj ustanovi?

696
00:35:02,032 --> 00:35:04,330
Ne. Vlasnik je ponatog restorana
u Hollywood-u...

697
00:35:04,367 --> 00:35:05,629
i postovan je gradjanin.

698
00:35:05,669 --> 00:35:08,934
Uradio sam veliku studiju o
psihologiji neuobicajenog...

699
00:35:08,972 --> 00:35:12,305
i iz tog iskustva znam iluzija
je izazov...

700
00:35:12,342 --> 00:35:13,934
a zabuna stvara nasilje.

701
00:35:13,977 --> 00:35:15,945
Ne slazem se sa vama,
ponovo.

702
00:35:15,979 --> 00:35:18,777
Ako kazete Krisu
da ne postoji Deda Mraz...

703
00:35:18,815 --> 00:35:21,249
On ce se sporiti sa vama,
ali nece biti nasilan.

704
00:35:21,284 --> 00:35:23,479
Njegov manir je ne-nasilje!

705
00:35:23,520 --> 00:35:26,387
Vidite kako cuva taj stap!
Nigde bez njega.

706
00:35:26,423 --> 00:35:28,823
Kris
uvek nosi svoj stap...

707
00:35:28,858 --> 00:35:31,326
ali nemojte reci, da ga koristi
kao oruzje!?

708
00:35:31,361 --> 00:35:35,457
Gospodjo Walker, naravno, mogu 
ga kompromitovati.

709
00:35:35,498 --> 00:35:39,025
Zavisi od vas. Ali,
trazili ste moje misljenje.

710
00:35:39,069 --> 00:35:40,969
Ako pokaze svoje latentne 
agresivne namere...

711
00:35:41,004 --> 00:35:42,938
a uveravam vas da hoce...

712
00:35:42,973 --> 00:35:45,601
shvatite, bice
vasa odgovornost.

713
00:35:51,081 --> 00:35:53,311
Ako pricamo o
iluzijama...

714
00:35:53,350 --> 00:35:55,682
Ponovo smo na pocetku.

715
00:35:55,719 --> 00:35:57,186
Ne, nismo.

716
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:59,654
Posle izlaganja Dr. Pierce-a,
Sasvim sam siguran.

717
00:35:59,689 --> 00:36:02,715
Ako se bilo sta dogodi. Vi necete
boti krivi. Bicu samo ja.

718
00:36:02,759 --> 00:36:05,353
Nista se nece dogoditi.

719
00:36:05,395 --> 00:36:07,989
I nemojte misliti da sam 
nesto rekao u afektu.

720
00:36:08,031 --> 00:36:09,999
Moja specijalnost je
gerijatrija.

721
00:36:10,033 --> 00:36:11,330
Hm?

722
00:36:11,368 --> 00:36:12,926
Lecenje bolesti poznih
godina.

723
00:36:12,969 --> 00:36:14,994
Imam prilicno iskustva...

724
00:36:15,038 --> 00:36:19,202
i uveravam vas Kris nema 
agresivnih namera.

725
00:36:19,242 --> 00:36:20,937
Verovatno cete zeleti da
pricate sa gosp. Shellhammer...

726
00:36:20,977 --> 00:36:23,537
pa, da krenem.
Mogu li videti Krisa?

727
00:36:23,580 --> 00:36:25,047
Naravno, doktore.

728
00:36:25,081 --> 00:36:26,946
Idite liftom za zaposlene.
Brze je.

729
00:36:26,983 --> 00:36:28,450
Istim kojim ste dosli.

730
00:36:28,485 --> 00:36:30,851
- Gde je to?
- Pokazacu vam.

731
00:36:30,887 --> 00:36:32,684
Nije potrebno.
Snacicu se.

732
00:36:32,722 --> 00:36:35,213
Razumete me, doktore...

733
00:36:35,258 --> 00:36:36,782
Ukoliko postoji
mogucnost...

734
00:36:36,826 --> 00:36:39,351
da postane nasilan ili
izazove nevolje...

735
00:36:39,396 --> 00:36:41,330
Kakve nevolje?

736
00:36:41,364 --> 00:36:44,094
Dovoljno je da ga policajac pita
kako se zove.

737
00:36:44,134 --> 00:36:46,967
velika stvar.
Clang, clang! Bellevue!

738
00:36:47,003 --> 00:36:48,971
Mozete to spreciti,
jednostavno.

739
00:36:49,005 --> 00:36:51,064
Ako bi bio samo sa
nekim zaposlenim...

740
00:36:51,107 --> 00:36:53,302
nista se nece dogoditi.

741
00:36:53,343 --> 00:36:56,471
Vise bih voleo da ne ide
Great Neck vozom dva puta dnevno.

742
00:36:56,513 --> 00:36:57,980
To je resenje.

743
00:36:58,014 --> 00:37:00,073
Tako ce se kloniti 
nevolje.

744
00:37:00,116 --> 00:37:01,583
Brinuce se, na neki nacin,
o njemu.

745
00:37:01,618 --> 00:37:03,245
Da li ce se on sloziti?

746
00:37:03,286 --> 00:37:04,913
Pricacu sa njim.
Sigurno hoce.

747
00:37:04,954 --> 00:37:06,421
U tom slicaju, moze
ostati.

748
00:37:06,456 --> 00:37:08,048
Dobro. Hvala vam.

749
00:37:08,091 --> 00:37:10,924
Ovo je sedmi sprat,
hvala vam mnogo.

750
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:12,154
- Dovidjenja doktore
- Dovidjenja.

751
00:37:13,697 --> 00:37:16,257
Sigurno si donela pravu
odluku.

752
00:37:16,299 --> 00:37:19,097
Videcemo...
Ko ce mu iznajmiti sobu?

753
00:37:19,135 --> 00:37:20,261
Ti.

754
00:37:20,303 --> 00:37:22,931
Tvoj sin je na koledzu..
Njegova soba?

755
00:37:22,972 --> 00:37:25,964
Nemam nista protiv.
Vrlo rado.

756
00:37:26,009 --> 00:37:28,443
Siguran sam, godpodji Shellha-
mmer se nece dopasti.

757
00:37:28,478 --> 00:37:30,070
Ona je malo...

758
00:37:30,113 --> 00:37:32,081
Cekaj, imam ideju.

759
00:37:32,115 --> 00:37:34,049
Uvek pijemo martini
pre vecere.

760
00:37:34,084 --> 00:37:36,712
Dupliracu joj dozu
veceras.

761
00:37:36,753 --> 00:37:39,722
posle nekoliko doza,
malo ce smeksati.

762
00:37:39,756 --> 00:37:41,451
Ali Kris je na poslu
do 6:00.

763
00:37:41,491 --> 00:37:43,220
A u medjuvremenu?

764
00:37:43,259 --> 00:37:44,954
Pozovi ga kod sebe 
na veceru.

765
00:37:44,994 --> 00:37:48,054
Zvacu ga....
cim budem mogao

766
00:37:48,098 --> 00:37:49,463
Oh, ne.

767
00:37:49,499 --> 00:37:51,057
Ako to uradim zeni...

768
00:37:51,101 --> 00:37:53,001
imace glavobolje
ujutru...

769
00:37:53,036 --> 00:37:54,901
ti ih mozes imati veceras.

770
00:37:54,938 --> 00:37:56,633
U redu.

771
00:37:56,673 --> 00:37:59,005
Dovoljno je sat vremena.
Bice sve u redu.

772
00:38:00,009 --> 00:38:02,569
Dobro. Vrlo dobro.

773
00:38:02,612 --> 00:38:06,207
Sta se igras obicno
sa decom?

774
00:38:06,249 --> 00:38:09,946
Ne igram se bas.
Glupave igre.

775
00:38:09,986 --> 00:38:11,214
Stvarno?

776
00:38:11,254 --> 00:38:13,916
Kao danas. U podrumu su se 
igrali Zoo vrta...

777
00:38:13,957 --> 00:38:16,084
i svi su bili
zivotinje.

778
00:38:16,126 --> 00:38:19,425
Kada sam sisla, Homer...
on je bio cuvar...

779
00:38:19,462 --> 00:38:22,590
pitao me, "Koja si
ti zivotinja?""

780
00:38:22,632 --> 00:38:25,829
Rekla sam, nisam 
zivotinja, vec devojcica

781
00:38:25,869 --> 00:38:27,928
"Samo je zivotinjama dozvoljen
ulaz" rekao je

782
00:38:27,971 --> 00:38:29,836
Otisla sam gore

783
00:38:29,873 --> 00:38:32,137
Zasto nisi rekla da si
lav ili medved?

784
00:38:32,175 --> 00:38:34,075
Zato sto nisam lav,
a ni medved.

785
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:37,079
Ali i deca su,
samo deca...

786
00:38:37,113 --> 00:38:39,081
i pretvaraju se da se
zivotinje.

787
00:38:39,115 --> 00:38:41,447
Zato je ta igra
glupava.

788
00:38:41,484 --> 00:38:42,644
Ne mislim tako.

789
00:38:42,685 --> 00:38:45,119
Zvuci mi kao dobra igra.

790
00:38:45,155 --> 00:38:50,650
Da bi se igrao, potrebna
ti je masta.

791
00:38:50,693 --> 00:38:53,184
Znas li sta je
masta?

792
00:38:53,229 --> 00:38:54,491
Naravno.

793
00:38:54,531 --> 00:38:57,193
Kada vidis stvari koje 
ne postoje.

794
00:38:57,233 --> 00:39:00,828
To moze biti i 
iz drugih razloga.

795
00:39:00,870 --> 00:39:04,431
Za mene je masta...

796
00:39:04,474 --> 00:39:06,442
kao zemlja za sebe.

797
00:39:06,476 --> 00:39:09,604
Cula si za Britance ili
Francuze.

798
00:39:09,646 --> 00:39:11,614
Tako je i to zemlja maste...

799
00:39:11,648 --> 00:39:13,707
To je divno mesto.

800
00:39:13,750 --> 00:39:20,053
Kako bi napravila grudve u 
sred leta?

801
00:39:20,089 --> 00:39:24,219
Ili vozila autobus
5-om Avenijom?

802
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:26,820
Da li bi volela da imas
svoj brod...

803
00:39:26,863 --> 00:39:30,822
i da putujes do Kine 
i Australije?

804
00:39:30,867 --> 00:39:33,427
Da li bi volela da
budes Kip Slobode...

805
00:39:33,470 --> 00:39:35,802
ujutru,
a uvece...

806
00:39:35,839 --> 00:39:37,670
letis ka jugu sa
jatom gusaka?

807
00:39:40,043 --> 00:39:43,444
Jednostavno je.
Naravno, potrebna je praksa.

808
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:47,940
Ali prvo, treba da naucis 
da zamisljas.

809
00:39:47,984 --> 00:39:51,943
I kada sledeci put Homer pita,
"Koja si ti zivotinja?"

810
00:39:51,988 --> 00:39:53,956
Reci da si majmun.

811
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:55,958
Ne znam kako da
budem majmun.

812
00:39:55,992 --> 00:39:58,460
Naravno da znas.
Pokazacu ti.

813
00:39:58,495 --> 00:40:00,463
Savi se samo malo...

814
00:40:00,497 --> 00:40:02,465
Opusti ruke...

815
00:40:02,499 --> 00:40:05,059
Sada, desnu ruku gore..
... ovde.

816
00:40:05,101 --> 00:40:08,559
Sada se pocesi.
Tako je.

817
00:40:08,605 --> 00:40:11,574
Isplazi jezik...

818
00:40:11,608 --> 00:40:14,577
- Ovako?
- Tako je.

819
00:40:14,611 --> 00:40:16,476
Pocesi se...

820
00:40:16,513 --> 00:40:19,710
- Bla bla bla!
- Eeek!

821
00:40:19,749 --> 00:40:21,114
Eeek erp!

822
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:24,483
Haislip, Haislip, Sherman,
Mackenzie, and Haislip...

823
00:40:24,521 --> 00:40:25,988
bili su veoma ljubazni.

824
00:40:26,022 --> 00:40:29,583
Ali kao izuzetan advokat,
zelim svoju kancelariju.

825
00:40:29,626 --> 00:40:32,117
Stavi ovo za Suzan...

826
00:40:32,161 --> 00:40:34,425
Izvadi meso.
Gotovo je.

827
00:40:36,666 --> 00:40:38,497
Ne zaboravi da se
poceses.

828
00:40:38,535 --> 00:40:41,003
Jezik izbaci...

829
00:40:41,037 --> 00:40:43,471
Pricaj sa ostalim
majmunima.

830
00:40:43,506 --> 00:40:45,804
Sta se ovde dogadja?

831
00:40:45,842 --> 00:40:47,969
U toku je prva lekcija
pretvaranja.

832
00:40:48,011 --> 00:40:50,002
Da, vrlo smo dobri u tome.

833
00:40:50,046 --> 00:40:53,015
Tako je. Zovi ostale
majmune.

834
00:40:53,049 --> 00:40:57,509
Ne. Nemoj biti guska.
Budi majmun.

835
00:40:57,554 --> 00:41:00,318
- Gospodine Kringle...
- Da?

836
00:41:00,356 --> 00:41:02,381
Gospodja Walker
je bas pomenula...

837
00:41:02,425 --> 00:41:04,620
da traze smestaj za vas.

838
00:41:04,661 --> 00:41:05,958
Tako je.

839
00:41:05,995 --> 00:41:08,589
Dr. Pierce ne zeli da puno 
putujem svakog dana.

840
00:41:08,631 --> 00:41:10,462
Nesto sam mislio...

841
00:41:10,500 --> 00:41:13,492
Ja sam sam u stanu.

842
00:41:13,536 --> 00:41:15,970
Dva kreveta, velika soba.

843
00:41:16,005 --> 00:41:18,974
Ako biste zeleli da se uselite
kod mene...

844
00:41:19,008 --> 00:41:20,976
Bio bih veoma srecan

845
00:41:21,010 --> 00:41:22,637
To je jako lepo od vas.

846
00:41:22,679 --> 00:41:25,580
Mogli bi ste na posao i
s posla sa gdjom. Walker.

847
00:41:25,615 --> 00:41:28,812
Da. To bi bila prilika
da...

848
00:41:28,851 --> 00:41:31,388
porazgovaram sa njom
o mnogo cemu.

849
00:41:33,857 --> 00:41:37,884
Ne zaboravi da se ceses.
Ne ceses se.

850
00:41:37,927 --> 00:41:40,657
I mogao bih vidjati
Suzan povremeno.

851
00:41:40,697 --> 00:41:42,494
Gospodine Gailey, 
dogovoreno.

852
00:41:42,532 --> 00:41:43,965
Odlicno!

853
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:47,299
Donecemo vase stvari
posle vecere.

854
00:41:47,337 --> 00:41:49,567
Halo,
samo trenutak.

855
00:41:49,606 --> 00:41:51,096
To je gospodin Shellhammer.

856
00:41:51,141 --> 00:41:52,301
Hvala.

857
00:41:53,376 --> 00:41:55,139
Pozdrav, gospodine 
Shellhammer.

858
00:41:55,178 --> 00:41:57,305
Da. Momenat.

859
00:41:57,347 --> 00:41:59,542
Gospodja Shellhammer
zeli da prica sa vama.

860
00:42:00,850 --> 00:42:03,444
Napravio sam martinije, 
trostruka doza...

861
00:42:03,486 --> 00:42:05,477
i ona se oseca
fantasticno.

862
00:42:06,790 --> 00:42:08,451
Izvoli, draga.

863
00:42:08,491 --> 00:42:10,254
Ha ha.

864
00:42:10,293 --> 00:42:11,783
Halo?

865
00:42:13,296 --> 00:42:14,763
Halo?

866
00:42:14,798 --> 00:42:16,766
Ne, ne. ne, draga.

867
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:19,098
Hvala, draga.

868
00:42:20,937 --> 00:42:22,802
Halo?

869
00:42:22,839 --> 00:42:25,637
Ne, ne draga. Ovde.

870
00:42:25,675 --> 00:42:28,838
Oh, dragi, kako glupavo
s moje strane!

871
00:42:30,513 --> 00:42:32,140
Halo!

872
00:42:33,917 --> 00:42:38,445
Voleli bi smo da Deda Mraz 
dodje kod nas.

873
00:42:40,356 --> 00:42:43,553
To bi bas bilo
sarmantno.

874
00:42:43,593 --> 00:42:45,993
Oh, i ja mislim gospodjo
Shellhammer.

875
00:42:46,029 --> 00:42:47,997
Samo malo.

876
00:42:48,031 --> 00:42:51,000
Ovde gospodja Shellhammer.
Imaju divnu sobu.

877
00:42:51,034 --> 00:42:53,093
Bili bi presrecni, da
budete kod njih.

878
00:42:53,136 --> 00:42:55,104
Vrlo lepo od njih.

879
00:42:55,138 --> 00:42:56,469
molim vas, zahvalite
im se...

880
00:42:56,506 --> 00:42:59,964
ali bicu kod
gospodina Gailey-ja.

881
00:43:00,009 --> 00:43:01,135
Gospodina Gailey-ja.

882
00:43:01,177 --> 00:43:03,873
Idem da pogledam
meso.

883
00:43:06,649 --> 00:43:08,276
Da, razumem...

884
00:43:08,318 --> 00:43:10,445
ali sigurno nesto zelis
za Bozic...

885
00:43:10,487 --> 00:43:12,955
nesto sto nisi rekla
ni svojoj majci.

886
00:43:12,989 --> 00:43:15,253
'ajde sad.

887
00:43:15,291 --> 00:43:17,316
Pruzi mi priliku.

888
00:43:18,862 --> 00:43:20,853
Pa..

889
00:43:37,614 --> 00:43:39,844
To zelim za
Bozic.

890
00:43:39,883 --> 00:43:41,510
Kucicu za lutke?

891
00:43:41,551 --> 00:43:44,145
Ne, pravu kucu.

892
00:43:44,187 --> 00:43:46,348
Ako si pravi Deda Mraz, to
ces mi omoguciti.

893
00:43:46,389 --> 00:43:47,617
A ako ne mozes...

894
00:43:47,657 --> 00:43:50,353
samo si fin covek sa belom 
bradom, kako mama kaze.

895
00:43:50,393 --> 00:43:51,985
Cekaj, Suzi.

896
00:43:52,028 --> 00:43:54,326
Samo zato sto svako dete
ne dobije ono sto zeli...

897
00:43:54,364 --> 00:43:55,831
Ne znaci da Deda Mraz
ne postoji.

898
00:43:55,865 --> 00:43:58,197
Znala sam da ces to reci.

899
00:43:58,234 --> 00:43:59,997
Zar ne shvatas, draga?

900
00:44:00,036 --> 00:44:02,937
Neka deca mastaju o 
stvarima koje ne mogu...

901
00:44:02,972 --> 00:44:05,668
imati. Kao lokomotivu,

902
00:44:05,708 --> 00:44:09,269
ili B-29.

903
00:44:09,312 --> 00:44:11,872
To su velike stvari za
devojcicu kao stio si ti.

904
00:44:11,915 --> 00:44:14,611
Sta bi ti sa takvom kucom?

905
00:44:14,651 --> 00:44:16,482
Zivela bih, sa 
mojom mamom.

906
00:44:16,519 --> 00:44:18,783
Ali, imas prelep
stan.

907
00:44:18,821 --> 00:44:20,448
Ne mislim da je narocito
lep.

908
00:44:20,490 --> 00:44:24,893
Zelim dvoriste sa velikim
drvetom, za ljuljasku...

909
00:44:28,498 --> 00:44:30,363
Izgleda mi to ne mozes
priustiti, a?

910
00:44:30,400 --> 00:44:32,834
Nisam to rekao.

911
00:44:32,869 --> 00:44:34,359
Pa...

912
00:44:39,008 --> 00:44:41,977
To je velika narudzbina...

913
00:44:42,011 --> 00:44:43,979
Dacu sve od sebe.

914
00:44:44,013 --> 00:44:45,640
Mogu li da zadrzim
sliku?

915
00:44:45,682 --> 00:44:47,377
Mm-hmm.

916
00:44:47,417 --> 00:44:50,875
Hvala. laku noc, Suzan.

917
00:44:50,920 --> 00:44:52,911
Laku noc, gospodine Kringle.

918
00:45:40,503 --> 00:45:42,471
Lepo vam je ovde.

919
00:45:42,505 --> 00:45:44,473
Srecan sam sto sam uspeo
da ga dobijem!

920
00:45:44,507 --> 00:45:47,908
Zivite na Manhattan-u?

921
00:45:47,944 --> 00:45:49,912
Tako je.

922
00:45:49,946 --> 00:45:52,278
Jednog dana, voleo bih
da zivim na Long Island-u.

923
00:45:52,315 --> 00:45:53,646
Ne veliku kucu.

924
00:45:53,683 --> 00:45:56,914
Jednu od onih malenih, u blizini
Manhasset-a.

925
00:45:56,953 --> 00:46:00,480
Znam na sta mislite.

926
00:46:00,523 --> 00:46:03,856
Jedna od onih
Colonial kucica.

927
00:46:03,893 --> 00:46:06,361
To ili Cape Cod.

928
00:46:06,396 --> 00:46:08,864
U pravu ste u vezi sa
gospodjom Walker.

929
00:46:08,898 --> 00:46:10,889
Sa malo vise truda...

930
00:46:10,933 --> 00:46:13,902
Mogla bi izaci iz
svoje skoljke.

931
00:46:13,936 --> 00:46:15,927
Izvedite je na veceru,
u pozoriste.

932
00:46:15,972 --> 00:46:17,599
Probao sam vec.

933
00:46:17,640 --> 00:46:19,904
Uvek je previse
zauzeta.

934
00:46:19,942 --> 00:46:22,570
Potrudite se vise.
Dve izgubljene duse.

935
00:46:22,612 --> 00:46:24,443
Na nama je da im
pomognemo.

936
00:46:24,480 --> 00:46:27,449
Ja cu se pobrinuti za Suzi,
a vi za majku.

937
00:46:27,483 --> 00:46:29,451
- Dogovoreno
- U redu?

938
00:46:29,485 --> 00:46:31,953
O, ne. Necete me
prevariti.

939
00:46:31,988 --> 00:46:34,081
Ceo zivot se pitam...

940
00:46:34,123 --> 00:46:36,091
I evo prilike
da saznam

941
00:46:36,125 --> 00:46:38,593
To je vekovna zagonetka.

942
00:46:38,628 --> 00:46:43,429
Da li Deda Mraz spava
sa svojim bicevima?

943
00:46:43,466 --> 00:46:45,434
Bez njih.

944
00:46:45,468 --> 00:46:47,459
Od hladnoce, porastu.

945
00:46:53,843 --> 00:46:55,470
Joe, ostacemo bez knjiga.

946
00:46:55,511 --> 00:46:57,103
Donecu, odmah.

947
00:46:57,146 --> 00:46:58,977
Treba mi jos 
Wanamakers-a.

948
00:47:22,972 --> 00:47:25,440
Znam sta vam je potrebno.

949
00:47:25,475 --> 00:47:28,444
Nemamo tog proizvodjaca,
ali kod Gimbels-a imaju.

950
00:47:28,478 --> 00:47:31,936
Da vidimo. Evo ga.

951
00:47:31,981 --> 00:47:34,575
Misli sam da sam vec
primetio. 2.98.

952
00:47:34,617 --> 00:47:36,448
Specijalna ponuda.

953
00:47:36,486 --> 00:47:38,454
Stvarno jeste. Hvala
vam.

954
00:47:38,488 --> 00:47:40,319
Nema na cemu.

955
00:47:48,865 --> 00:47:50,958
Zasto se neko od vas
nije toga setio?

956
00:47:51,000 --> 00:47:54,401
To je najbolja
strategija dobre volje za

957
00:47:54,437 --> 00:47:56,371
koju sam cuo. Svaki
kupac u New York City-ju...

958
00:47:56,405 --> 00:47:59,499
misli o Macy-ju
kao o dobroj dusi...

959
00:47:59,542 --> 00:48:02,534
koja misli na dobrobit
potrosaca.

960
00:48:02,578 --> 00:48:04,409
A sta cini Gimbel?

961
00:48:04,447 --> 00:48:06,415
Samo profit i otimanje
novca.

962
00:48:06,449 --> 00:48:08,417
Dvoje mogu igrati
ovu igru.

963
00:48:08,451 --> 00:48:11,420
Od sada, ako nemamo sta kupac
zeli...

964
00:48:11,454 --> 00:48:12,921
posaljimo ga kod
Macy-ja.

965
00:48:12,955 --> 00:48:15,389
I vise od toga,, u svim nasim
prodavnicama...

966
00:48:15,424 --> 00:48:18,052
u Philadelphia-ji,
Milwaukee-ju, i Pittsburgh-u.

967
00:48:18,094 --> 00:48:20,062
Odmah na posao.

968
00:48:22,031 --> 00:48:24,693
Tako znaci, Gimbel's to cini i
u Philadelphia-ji...

969
00:48:24,734 --> 00:48:26,429
Pittsburgh-u i Milwaukee-ju, ha?

970
00:48:26,469 --> 00:48:27,936
I to vrlo uspesno.

971
00:48:27,970 --> 00:48:30,029
I mi mozemo to, u celoj
zemlji.

972
00:48:30,072 --> 00:48:32,063
Obavesti sve u prodavnicama
u San Francisco-u...

973
00:48:32,108 --> 00:48:35,566
Atlanta-i, Toledo-u i  Newark-u.

974
00:48:35,611 --> 00:48:37,078
U redu gospodine Macy.

975
00:48:38,247 --> 00:48:41,375
- Pogledajte ovamo gospodine
 Gimbel. 

976
00:48:41,417 --> 00:48:43,146
Jos jednom.

977
00:48:43,186 --> 00:48:44,983
To je dobro.

978
00:48:45,021 --> 00:48:47,421
Uradicemo neke i u 
prodavnici.

979
00:48:47,456 --> 00:48:48,889
Samo malo.

980
00:48:48,925 --> 00:48:52,383
Zeleo bih nesto da dam
nasem prijatelju.

981
00:48:52,428 --> 00:48:56,364
Mali poklon, u znak
zahvalnosti...

982
00:48:56,399 --> 00:48:57,525
za ono sto ste ucinili.

983
00:48:57,567 --> 00:48:59,797
Hvala gospodine Macy.

984
00:48:59,836 --> 00:49:02,737
Ooh! Vrlo ljubazno od vas.

985
00:49:02,772 --> 00:49:05,900
Nisam znao da ste tako
darezljivi.

986
00:49:05,942 --> 00:49:07,910
To je lepa svota novca.

987
00:49:07,944 --> 00:49:09,912
Sta cete sa njim?

988
00:49:09,946 --> 00:49:13,575
Pa, imam prijatelja.

989
00:49:13,616 --> 00:49:16,414
Doktora. Bio je veoma
ljubazan prema meni.

990
00:49:16,452 --> 00:49:18,420
Potreban mu ultra zvuk.

991
00:49:18,454 --> 00:49:20,855
To nece biti dovoljno.

992
00:49:20,988 --> 00:49:23,616
Dodacu, koliko je
potrebno.

993
00:49:23,657 --> 00:49:25,625
Kupite u prodavnici.
Dobicete 10% popusta.

994
00:49:25,659 --> 00:49:28,059
Platicu punu cenu.

995
00:49:34,335 --> 00:49:36,030
Laku noc, Suzan.

996
00:49:36,070 --> 00:49:37,799
Laku noc, Kleo.

997
00:49:37,838 --> 00:49:41,296
Hoces da ti otpevam
uspavanku?

998
00:49:41,342 --> 00:49:43,310
Ako zelis.

999
00:49:43,344 --> 00:49:46,313
Da li ti je mama nekada pevala
pred spavanje?

1000
00:49:46,347 --> 00:49:49,077
Mhhm. Zasto bi?

1001
00:49:49,116 --> 00:49:53,951
Pa, onako.
Mislim da je to bas lepo.

1002
00:49:53,988 --> 00:49:57,287
- Da li volis "Market"?
- Moze.

1003
00:49:57,324 --> 00:50:01,351
To market, to market
to buy a fat pig

1004
00:50:01,395 --> 00:50:04,626
Home again, home again,
jiggidy jig

1005
00:50:04,665 --> 00:50:08,066
To market, to market
to buy a fat hog

1006
00:50:08,102 --> 00:50:11,970
Home again, home again,
jiggidy...

1007
00:50:16,644 --> 00:50:19,044
Neverovatno.

1008
00:50:19,079 --> 00:50:21,240
Imas li mozda rezervnu?

1009
00:50:21,282 --> 00:50:22,579
Mm-hmm.

1010
00:50:32,593 --> 00:50:34,424
Evo je.

1011
00:50:45,673 --> 00:50:48,301
Oh!

1012
00:51:03,924 --> 00:51:05,755
- Zdravo, Alfred.
- Zdravo, Kris.

1013
00:51:05,793 --> 00:51:08,591
Sta kazes o jednoj igri
posle rucka?

1014
00:51:08,629 --> 00:51:11,757
Nemoj danas.
Nisam raspolozen.

1015
00:51:11,799 --> 00:51:13,596
Oh? Sta se dogodilo?

1016
00:51:13,634 --> 00:51:15,363
Nista. Nista.

1017
00:51:15,403 --> 00:51:18,065
Nesto nije u redu.
Sta je bilo?

1018
00:51:19,640 --> 00:51:22,473
Pa, secas se
pricao sam ti...

1019
00:51:22,510 --> 00:51:25,809
Kako volim da glumim Deda Mraza
u "Y" za Bozic...

1020
00:51:25,846 --> 00:51:28,144
i delim paketice
deci?

1021
00:51:28,182 --> 00:51:30,650
Rekao sam to i gospodinu
Sawyer-u, i...

1022
00:51:30,685 --> 00:51:33,552
on kaze da to nije dobro.

1023
00:51:33,587 --> 00:51:35,282
Sawyer. Mislis, uh...

1024
00:51:35,323 --> 00:51:38,292
Bas taj.
On je psihijatar.

1025
00:51:38,326 --> 00:51:41,295
Ohh,
to je diskutabilno...

1026
00:51:41,329 --> 00:51:43,194
Zasto je to lose, 
sta kaze?

1027
00:51:43,230 --> 00:51:47,792
Kaze oni koji se oblace kao 
Deda Mraz...

1028
00:51:47,835 --> 00:51:49,302
i daju poklone...

1029
00:51:49,337 --> 00:51:51,305
to rade zato sto
kada su bili mali...

1030
00:51:51,339 --> 00:51:52,806
sigurno su uradili
nesto jako lose...

1031
00:51:52,840 --> 00:51:54,239
I osecaju krivicu
zbog toga.

1032
00:51:54,275 --> 00:51:56,402
I sada bi da cine nesto,
za sta misle da je dobro...

1033
00:51:56,444 --> 00:51:57,741
Da se iskupe.

1034
00:51:57,778 --> 00:52:00,542
On to naziva
kompleks krivice.

1035
00:52:02,783 --> 00:52:04,546
Koliko imas godina, Alfred?

1036
00:52:04,585 --> 00:52:06,052
Sedamnaest.

1037
00:52:06,087 --> 00:52:08,248
Sedamnaest.

1038
00:52:08,289 --> 00:52:10,917
Izgleda nije bilo vremena
da toliko zgresis...

1039
00:52:10,958 --> 00:52:12,482
osim preterivanja.

1040
00:52:12,526 --> 00:52:14,756
Nije to smesno.

1041
00:52:14,795 --> 00:52:16,888
On kaze da 
je to vrlo ozbiljno.

1042
00:52:16,931 --> 00:52:19,229
Gomila gluposti, Alfred.
Ne slusaj ga.

1043
00:52:19,266 --> 00:52:21,257
Oh, on zna
o cemu govori.

1044
00:52:21,302 --> 00:52:24,100
On je to studirao, 
prilicno dugo.

1045
00:52:24,138 --> 00:52:27,767
Sta je osnova kompleksa
krivice...

1046
00:52:27,808 --> 00:52:29,435
koji ti, navodno, imas?

1047
00:52:29,477 --> 00:52:31,001
Da li ti je rekao?

1048
00:52:31,045 --> 00:52:34,276
Pa, nije ga jos
pronasao.

1049
00:52:34,315 --> 00:52:37,773
Verovatno je negde
prikriven.

1050
00:52:37,818 --> 00:52:41,015
Mozda kada sam bio jos 
beba, kaze.

1051
00:52:41,055 --> 00:52:44,149
Potrebno je vreme, Ali, 
naci ce on vec.

1052
00:52:44,191 --> 00:52:47,024
Ponovo ces ici kod njega?

1053
00:52:47,061 --> 00:52:50,121
Naravno. Idem svaki dan 
posle rucka.

1054
00:52:50,164 --> 00:52:52,530
Nista mi ne naplacuje.

1055
00:52:52,566 --> 00:52:56,229
Zato sto sam zanimljiv
slucaj.

1056
00:52:56,270 --> 00:52:57,464
Da.

1057
00:52:57,505 --> 00:53:00,372
Sta je jos lose pronasao
kod tebe, Alfred?

1058
00:53:01,442 --> 00:53:03,342
Jos nesto?

1059
00:53:03,377 --> 00:53:06,437
Nista. Samo da... mrzim oca.

1060
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:09,449
Nisam ni znao,
ali on tako kaze.

1061
00:53:09,483 --> 00:53:11,849
I svaki dan te vidja?

1062
00:53:11,886 --> 00:53:15,344
Da. Pricam mu sve
sto mi padne napamet.

1063
00:53:15,389 --> 00:53:17,254
Izvini, Alfred.

1064
00:53:17,291 --> 00:53:18,952
Nesto mi je palo
na pamet...

1065
00:53:18,993 --> 00:53:20,517
I moram ih izgovoriti.

1066
00:53:32,072 --> 00:53:33,869
Zasto si ti ovde?

1067
00:53:33,908 --> 00:53:35,967
Imas li ti diplomu psihijatra?

1068
00:53:36,010 --> 00:53:38,205
Zasto to tebe zanima?

1069
00:53:38,245 --> 00:53:40,270
Veoma postujem 
psihijatriju...

1070
00:53:40,314 --> 00:53:43,306
i prezirem amatere
koji je upraznjavaju.

1071
00:53:43,350 --> 00:53:45,284
Nemas prava da ...

1072
00:53:45,319 --> 00:53:47,617
Analiziras Alfreda!

1073
00:53:47,655 --> 00:53:48,952
Molim?

1074
00:53:48,989 --> 00:53:52,254
Tvoj posao ovde je da
dajes testove inteligencije.

1075
00:53:52,293 --> 00:53:54,158
Ne izdaj se za 
psihijatra.

1076
00:53:54,195 --> 00:53:56,425
Trebalo bi te pritvoriti...

1077
00:53:56,464 --> 00:53:58,728
jednog normalnog, zdravog 
momka, kao sto je Alfred

1078
00:53:58,766 --> 00:54:00,529
Napuniti kompleksima
krivice.

1079
00:54:00,568 --> 00:54:02,900
Vise sam kompetentniji 
da prosudjujem od tebe.

1080
00:54:02,937 --> 00:54:05,235
Samo zato sto decko zeli da bude
dobar prema deci...

1081
00:54:05,272 --> 00:54:07,240
kazes mu da ima kompleks
krivice.

1082
00:54:07,274 --> 00:54:09,003
Delite istu iluziju, 
kako da razumes.

1083
00:54:09,043 --> 00:54:11,409
Alfred je nestabilan i potrebna
mu je moja pomoc.

1084
00:54:11,445 --> 00:54:12,912
Nestabilan?!
Ti govoris o nestabilnosti.

1085
00:54:12,947 --> 00:54:15,245
Ovo je kao da pacijent
vodi kliniku.

1086
00:54:15,282 --> 00:54:17,750
Dosta je bilo...
Odlazi, smesta.

1087
00:54:17,785 --> 00:54:19,946
Ili ces prestati da 
analiziras Alfreda...

1088
00:54:19,987 --> 00:54:21,454
ili idem kod
gospodina Macy-ja...

1089
00:54:21,489 --> 00:54:23,753
da mu kazem, kakav si
prevarant.

1090
00:54:23,791 --> 00:54:25,452
Odlazi, ili cu pozvati
obezbedjenje.

1091
00:54:25,493 --> 00:54:29,395
Samo je jedan nacin, sa takvima 
kao sto si ti.

1092
00:54:29,430 --> 00:54:31,830
Nisi razuman. I 
bezosecajan si.

1093
00:54:31,866 --> 00:54:32,992
Nemas ni malo ljudskosti.

1094
00:54:33,033 --> 00:54:35,228
Hoces li izaci?

1095
00:54:35,269 --> 00:54:36,463
Da.

1096
00:54:45,646 --> 00:54:46,943
- Kris.
- Gospodine Sawyer!

1097
00:54:46,981 --> 00:54:49,449
Gospodine Sawyer,
da li ste dobro?

1098
00:54:49,483 --> 00:54:50,677
Pogledaj modricu!

1099
00:54:50,718 --> 00:54:51,946
Gospodine Sawyer...
On je bez svesti!

1100
00:54:51,986 --> 00:54:53,886
Brzo mokar peskir.

1101
00:54:53,921 --> 00:54:55,388
Bolje da pozovemo
doktora.

1102
00:54:55,422 --> 00:54:57,890
Sigurno ste mu nesto
uradili.

1103
00:54:57,925 --> 00:54:59,893
Jedva i da smo
razgovarali...

1104
00:54:59,927 --> 00:55:03,124
Pomenuo sam Deda Mraza i
ugrozio njegovu iluziju...

1105
00:55:03,163 --> 00:55:04,391
Postao je nasilan.

1106
00:55:04,431 --> 00:55:06,899
Rekao sam vam latentno je
agresivan.

1107
00:55:06,934 --> 00:55:08,902
Ovo je dokaz.

1108
00:55:08,936 --> 00:55:11,404
Neka ga Dr. Pierce
ponovo pregleda.

1109
00:55:11,438 --> 00:55:12,564
Dr. Pierce...

1110
00:55:12,606 --> 00:55:14,904
On ne zna nista
o tome.

1111
00:55:14,942 --> 00:55:16,409
On je lekar
opste prakse.

1112
00:55:16,443 --> 00:55:18,411
Priznacete, ovo je prilicno
ozbiljno.

1113
00:55:18,445 --> 00:55:19,912
Bolje da pozovemo psihijatra.

1114
00:55:19,947 --> 00:55:22,415
Ali imao je bezbroj
pregleda...

1115
00:55:22,449 --> 00:55:23,916
i sve ih je prosao, i
to 100%.

1116
00:55:23,951 --> 00:55:26,647
Mozda mu se stanje promenilo.

1117
00:55:26,687 --> 00:55:28,917
Ne smemo da rizikujemo.

1118
00:55:28,956 --> 00:55:30,924
Ne vidim problem
u tome.

1119
00:55:30,958 --> 00:55:33,483
Ako prodje test,
moze da se vrati na posao...

1120
00:55:33,527 --> 00:55:35,927
a ako ne, bolje da to 
saznamo.

1121
00:55:35,963 --> 00:55:38,431
Bolje da ga pregledaju
sto pre...

1122
00:55:38,465 --> 00:55:41,434
pre nego sto kaze gospodinu Ma...
pre nego sto gosp. Macy sazna.

1123
00:55:41,468 --> 00:55:42,594
O, da...

1124
00:55:42,636 --> 00:55:45,434
Objasnote gospodinu Kringle-u.
Najzad, vi ste mu prijatelj.

1125
00:55:45,472 --> 00:55:48,100
Necu. Jako mi
je drag.

1126
00:55:48,142 --> 00:55:51,441
To bi bilo kao da mu
kazem da je lud.

1127
00:55:51,478 --> 00:55:53,878
Ali ovo nije
normalno ponasanje.

1128
00:55:53,914 --> 00:55:55,438
Naravno da nije...

1129
00:55:55,482 --> 00:55:57,882
Ali mnogi stariji ljudi, nisu 
sasvim pri sebi.

1130
00:55:57,918 --> 00:56:00,944
To ce Krisa povrediti,
a ja to ne zelim!

1131
00:56:08,762 --> 00:56:10,730
To ne bi bilo fer.

1132
00:56:10,764 --> 00:56:12,231
Reci cu mu istinu.

1133
00:56:12,266 --> 00:56:14,393
Treba biti iskren.

1134
00:56:14,435 --> 00:56:16,733
Ako me vidi, ili pomenes
psihijatra...

1135
00:56:16,770 --> 00:56:19,398
to je, opet napad
na njegovu iluziju.

1136
00:56:19,440 --> 00:56:20,907
Postace nasilan.

1137
00:56:20,941 --> 00:56:22,408
Pred decom?

1138
00:56:22,443 --> 00:56:23,910
To bi bilo strasno.

1139
00:56:23,944 --> 00:56:26,742
Izvedi ga iz prodavnice.

1140
00:56:26,780 --> 00:56:28,907
Napolju cu mu
objasniti.

1141
00:56:28,949 --> 00:56:30,940
Bolje je tako.

1142
00:56:32,486 --> 00:56:35,387
Budite u redu..
Svi cete videti Deda Mraza.

1143
00:56:37,958 --> 00:56:39,255
Oh!

1144
00:56:41,962 --> 00:56:43,259
- Gospodine Kringle.
- Da?

1145
00:56:43,297 --> 00:56:44,924
Gospodja Walker
zeli da znate...

1146
00:56:44,965 --> 00:56:46,933
da cemo napraviti nekoliko
snimaka danas...

1147
00:56:46,967 --> 00:56:49,765
u skupstini...

1148
00:56:49,803 --> 00:56:50,929
vi i gradonacelnik.

1149
00:56:50,971 --> 00:56:52,438
Dobro. Drago mi je da cu ga
videti.

1150
00:56:52,473 --> 00:56:54,873
Hteo bih da popricamo o necemu...

1151
00:56:54,908 --> 00:56:58,366
Oh, ali, imam zakazano kod
gospodina Macy-ja u 4:00.

1152
00:56:58,412 --> 00:57:00,380
Zelim i njemu nesto 
da kazem.

1153
00:57:00,414 --> 00:57:02,882
Brzo cete se vratiti.

1154
00:57:02,916 --> 00:57:04,383
Cekaju vas kola dole.

1155
00:57:04,418 --> 00:57:06,352
Pocinje da biva hladno.
Trebace vam kaput.

1156
00:57:06,387 --> 00:57:07,513
Ponecu ga.

1157
00:57:07,554 --> 00:57:08,987
Hvala. Odmah dolazim.

1158
00:57:09,023 --> 00:57:11,890
Samo da se pobrinem za nekoliko 
malisana.

1159
00:57:11,925 --> 00:57:13,415
U redu.

1160
00:57:36,717 --> 00:57:38,207
Kuda?

1161
00:57:38,252 --> 00:57:39,719
Bellevue.

1162
00:57:39,753 --> 00:57:40,981
Bellevue?!

1163
00:57:49,797 --> 00:57:51,498
Da li ona zna za ovo?

1164
00:57:51,631 --> 00:57:54,464
Da.
Pricali smo o tome.

1165
00:58:03,376 --> 00:58:04,843
Drugi deo pokazuje...

1166
00:58:04,878 --> 00:58:06,846
S obzirom na...

1167
00:58:06,880 --> 00:58:08,848
saglasnost, prvog...

1168
00:58:08,882 --> 00:58:11,442
Izvinite, Gertrude. Telefon.

1169
00:58:13,887 --> 00:58:15,354
Halo.

1170
00:58:15,388 --> 00:58:17,379
Da. Da.

1171
00:58:18,424 --> 00:58:20,824
Zasto, da,
zivimo u istom stanu.

1172
00:58:23,096 --> 00:58:24,222
Bellevue?

1173
00:58:24,264 --> 00:58:27,097
Ali zasto, doctore? Sta je...

1174
00:58:27,133 --> 00:58:29,067
Prilicno je dobro.

1175
00:58:29,102 --> 00:58:32,071
Bice sa nama nekoliko
dana...

1176
00:58:32,105 --> 00:58:35,074
ako mozete da donesete
njegove licne stvari.

1177
00:58:35,108 --> 00:58:38,566
Da, nekoliko pregleda...

1178
00:58:38,611 --> 00:58:42,877
Bojim se da cu morati da 
predlozim da ostane.

1179
00:58:42,916 --> 00:58:44,884
Da, znam, gospodine Gailey...

1180
00:58:44,918 --> 00:58:46,783
Radije bih sa vama popricao
uzivo.

1181
00:58:46,819 --> 00:58:48,377
Odmah dolazim, doktore.

1182
00:58:55,361 --> 00:58:57,022
Za novog pacijenta.

1183
00:58:57,063 --> 00:58:58,724
- Hvala.
- Nema na cemu.

1184
00:59:08,241 --> 00:59:09,902
Zdravo, Kris.

1185
00:59:09,943 --> 00:59:11,843
Fred.

1186
00:59:11,878 --> 00:59:14,745
Zasto si to uradio, Kris?

1187
00:59:14,781 --> 00:59:17,773
Namerno si pao na testu, zar ne?

1188
00:59:19,752 --> 00:59:21,083
Zasto?

1189
00:59:21,120 --> 00:59:25,113
Poslednjih nekolika dana,
imao sam veliku nadu.

1190
00:59:25,158 --> 00:59:28,616
Mislio sam da je Doris pocela
da veruje u mene.

1191
00:59:28,661 --> 00:59:32,119
Sada vidim da mi se sve vreme
podsmevala.

1192
00:59:32,165 --> 00:59:33,632
Ali, sad sam pricao sa njom.

1193
00:59:33,666 --> 00:59:36,362
Nista nije znala o slikanju sa
gradonacelnikom.

1194
00:59:36,402 --> 00:59:38,370
To je Sawyer-ova ideja.

1195
00:59:38,404 --> 00:59:40,065
Drago mi je.

1196
00:59:40,106 --> 00:59:43,667
Zasto nije dosla da mi
sve objasni?

1197
00:59:43,710 --> 00:59:46,144
Ne zeli da te povredi.

1198
00:59:46,179 --> 00:59:49,376
Zato sto sam dobri,
stari cika koga joj je zao.

1199
00:59:49,415 --> 00:59:50,882
Nije istina.

1200
00:59:50,917 --> 00:59:52,782
Jeste.
Dvoumi se.

1201
00:59:52,819 --> 00:59:54,081
Zato joj je i zao.

1202
00:59:54,120 --> 00:59:56,088
Da su tebe ovde dovukli
umesto mene...

1203
00:59:56,122 --> 00:59:57,680
Ne bi joj bilo zao.

1204
00:59:57,724 --> 00:59:59,123
Bila bi ocajna.

1205
00:59:59,158 --> 01:00:02,184
U redu,
sumnjicava je. Zasto ne?

1206
01:00:02,228 --> 01:00:04,696
Ni u sta ne veruje godinama.

1207
01:00:04,731 --> 01:00:06,665
Ne mozes da ocekujes 
da odjednom...

1208
01:00:06,699 --> 01:00:09,532
Dobro, nije samo Doris.
I gospodin Sawyer.

1209
01:00:09,569 --> 01:00:14,529
On je nekompetentan, neiskren,
sebican, zloban...

1210
01:00:14,574 --> 01:00:17,202
Da, ali on je tamo, a ja sam ovde.

1211
01:00:17,243 --> 01:00:19,643
Njega nazivaju normalnim,
a mene ne.

1212
01:00:19,679 --> 01:00:21,704
Ako je to normalno. 
Ne zelim to.

1213
01:00:21,748 --> 01:00:24,717
Zato sam odgovarao netacno.

1214
01:00:24,751 --> 01:00:27,686
Ali, Kris, ne mozes da
mislis samo na sebe.

1215
01:00:27,720 --> 01:00:30,814
Ono sto ti se dogadja, tice se
mnogo ljudi.

1216
01:00:30,857 --> 01:00:34,384
Ljudi kao ja, koji veruju u
ono iza cega stojis...

1217
01:00:34,427 --> 01:00:37,726
i ljudi kao Suzie,
koji tek to pocinju.

1218
01:00:37,764 --> 01:00:40,892
Ne mozes odustati.
Ne mozes ih izneveriti.

1219
01:00:40,933 --> 01:00:42,833
Pretpostavljam, da ne.

1220
01:00:42,869 --> 01:00:45,702
Ko zna mozda ce Sawyers 
jednom biti ovde...

1221
01:00:45,738 --> 01:00:47,205
umesto tamo.

1222
01:00:47,240 --> 01:00:50,232
U pravu si.
Trebalo bi da se stidim.

1223
01:00:50,276 --> 01:00:53,803
Iako ne mozemo da pobedimo,
ne smemo odustati.

1224
01:00:53,846 --> 01:00:55,746
Hajdemo odavde.

1225
01:00:55,782 --> 01:00:57,249
Sad, sacekaj...

1226
01:00:57,283 --> 01:01:00,309
Zaboravio si da si pao na testu.

1227
01:01:00,353 --> 01:01:02,321
O, jesam.

1228
01:01:02,355 --> 01:01:04,721
Rekao sam da je Calvin Coolidge
bio prvi predsednik.

1229
01:01:04,757 --> 01:01:08,215
Mogu da zamislim, sta
su pomislili o meni.

1230
01:01:08,261 --> 01:01:10,229
Ali, ti ces me izvuci
odavde.

1231
01:01:10,263 --> 01:01:11,787
Smislices vec nesto.

1232
01:01:11,831 --> 01:01:13,298
Nece biti lako, Kris.

1233
01:01:13,332 --> 01:01:14,799
Bicu uz tebe.

1234
01:01:14,834 --> 01:01:17,268
Verujem da si najbolji advokat
jos od Darrow-a.

1235
01:01:17,303 --> 01:01:19,794
Samo malo, Kris.
Stavljas me u tezak polozaj.

1236
01:01:19,839 --> 01:01:22,899
Verujem u tebe.
Neces me izneveriti.

1237
01:01:22,942 --> 01:01:24,967
Ne razumes. To...

1238
01:01:27,313 --> 01:01:29,907
Ucinicu sve sto je moguce, Kris.

1239
01:01:29,949 --> 01:01:31,075
Hvala ti.

1240
01:01:31,117 --> 01:01:33,347
- Dovidjenja.
- Dovidjenja.

1241
01:01:37,857 --> 01:01:40,155
Gomila gluposti!
Opasnost, malo sutra!

1242
01:01:40,193 --> 01:01:42,320
Nije me briga i da je pao 
deset testova.

1243
01:01:42,361 --> 01:01:43,828
Nemas prava da to ucinis!

1244
01:01:43,863 --> 01:01:46,331
Dobices ovaj slucaj...

1245
01:01:46,365 --> 01:01:50,301
ili jos jednu modricu na glavi,
da se slaze sa onom

1246
01:01:50,336 --> 01:01:51,735
Sto ti je Kris dao.
U redu gospodine Macy.

1247
01:02:06,719 --> 01:02:08,243
Godiste - nepoznato.

1248
01:02:08,287 --> 01:02:09,720
Star covek, a?

1249
01:02:09,756 --> 01:02:11,724
Veoma star, 
Vasa Visosti.

1250
01:02:11,758 --> 01:02:14,454
Ovo sve treba da
procitam?

1251
01:02:14,494 --> 01:02:16,826
Verujte mi na rec.
Samo pogledajte.

1252
01:02:16,863 --> 01:02:18,330
Sve je jasno.

1253
01:02:18,364 --> 01:02:20,229
Naziva sebe
Kris Kringle...

1254
01:02:20,266 --> 01:02:21,995
Misli da je 
Deda Mraz.

1255
01:02:22,034 --> 01:02:23,296
Uh-oh.

1256
01:02:25,972 --> 01:02:27,234
Udjite.

1257
01:02:28,341 --> 01:02:30,639
Gospodin Gailey,
Vasa Visosti.

1258
01:02:30,676 --> 01:02:31,973
On zastupa gospodina Kringle-a.

1259
01:02:33,446 --> 01:02:34,777
Neka udje.

1260
01:02:37,617 --> 01:02:38,948
Dobro jutro.

1261
01:02:38,985 --> 01:02:41,579
Vasa Visosti, sta god da koci 
ovaj slucaj.

1262
01:02:41,621 --> 01:02:44,089
Zelim da zastitim prava svog 
klijenta. Kao i vi.

1263
01:02:44,123 --> 01:02:45,249
Naravno.

1264
01:02:45,291 --> 01:02:47,418
Trazio sam formalno
saslusanje...

1265
01:02:47,460 --> 01:02:49,121
na koje bih doveo svedoke.

1266
01:02:49,162 --> 01:02:51,790
- Sve je jasno?
- Tako mi je receno.

1267
01:02:51,831 --> 01:02:53,731
Nisam znao nista o
zalbi.

1268
01:02:53,766 --> 01:02:56,633
Naravno, mozete potpisati
papire odmah...

1269
01:02:56,669 --> 01:02:58,330
Donecu dokaze kasnije.

1270
01:02:58,371 --> 01:03:00,839
Nema svrhe potpisati.

1271
01:03:00,873 --> 01:03:05,537
Imacemo saslusanje
u ponedeljak u 10:00.

1272
01:03:05,578 --> 01:03:07,603
Hvala vam.

1273
01:03:12,285 --> 01:03:13,775
Hvala.

1274
01:03:18,790 --> 01:03:20,087
Taj covek...

1275
01:03:20,125 --> 01:03:23,253
Cuo sam da je govorio o
gospodinu Kringle-u.

1276
01:03:23,295 --> 01:03:24,762
Ko je on?

1277
01:03:24,796 --> 01:03:26,263
Gailey,
Kringle-ov advokat.

1278
01:03:26,298 --> 01:03:29,267
Verovatno zeli malo
publiciteta.

1279
01:03:29,301 --> 01:03:32,270
Nista od toga.
Gospodin Macy ne bi to voleo.

1280
01:03:32,304 --> 01:03:33,771
Nista. Sada je kasno.

1281
01:03:33,805 --> 01:03:36,273
Kringle-a su pregledali psihijatri 
gradske bolnice.

1282
01:03:36,308 --> 01:03:37,866
Tako to ide.

1283
01:03:37,909 --> 01:03:39,877
Moramo izbeci
publicitet.

1284
01:03:39,911 --> 01:03:41,401
Ja, uh... Oh.

1285
01:03:50,222 --> 01:03:52,884
Gospodine Gailey,
Ja zastupam gosp. Macy-ja.

1286
01:03:52,924 --> 01:03:54,323
Ime mi je Sawyer.

1287
01:03:54,359 --> 01:03:55,826
O, vi ste Sawyer.

1288
01:03:55,861 --> 01:03:57,886
Da. U vezi sa slucajem
Kringle...

1289
01:03:57,929 --> 01:04:00,056
Stalo nam je da izbegnemo
publicitet.

1290
01:04:00,098 --> 01:04:01,326
Naravno.

1291
01:04:01,366 --> 01:04:04,563
Ako se slazete, da uradimo to
sto je moguce tise...

1292
01:04:04,603 --> 01:04:07,834
Nacicemo nacina da iskazemo
nasu zahvalnost

1293
01:04:07,873 --> 01:04:09,033
Interesantno.

1294
01:04:09,074 --> 01:04:10,837
Saradjivacete?

1295
01:04:10,876 --> 01:04:13,743
Interesantno.
Publicitet. Hmm.

1296
01:04:13,779 --> 01:04:15,542
To i nije losa ideja.

1297
01:04:15,580 --> 01:04:17,411
Dobicu ovaj slucaj...

1298
01:04:17,449 --> 01:04:19,747
Imacu veliki broj
javnih misljenja.

1299
01:04:19,785 --> 01:04:22,083
A publicitet je jedan
od nacina, da to uradim.

1300
01:04:24,423 --> 01:04:26,891
Hvala gospodine Sawyer.

1301
01:04:26,925 --> 01:04:30,554
Oh, gospodine Gailey,
sacekajte...

1302
01:04:30,595 --> 01:04:33,086
Molim vas!

1303
01:04:58,423 --> 01:05:01,221
Ne vidim zasto ste toliko
uzbudjeni.

1304
01:05:01,259 --> 01:05:02,726
Ipak, on je jedan 
star covek.

1305
01:05:02,761 --> 01:05:04,729
Kako se vi osecate
u poslednje vreme?

1306
01:05:04,763 --> 01:05:06,355
Izgledate iznureno.

1307
01:05:06,398 --> 01:05:09,367
Ja? Zasto, dobro sam.
Nikad bolje.

1308
01:05:09,401 --> 01:05:11,869
Zasto ne odete do doktora?
Uzmite par nedelja slobodno.

1309
01:05:11,903 --> 01:05:14,872
Idite na pecanje, u lov.
Bilo gde.

1310
01:05:14,906 --> 01:05:16,874
Zasto bih?

1311
01:05:16,908 --> 01:05:18,899
Zato sto je Kringle-ov 
slicaj, pravi dinamit!

1312
01:05:18,944 --> 01:05:21,913
Nemojte reci da ne dolazi u pravo
vreme re-izbora?

1313
01:05:21,947 --> 01:05:23,380
Ne mogu ja to...

1314
01:05:23,415 --> 01:05:24,882
Nisam bas zadrti
legalista.

1315
01:05:24,916 --> 01:05:27,749
Ne razumem se u pravne 
termine.

1316
01:05:27,786 --> 01:05:30,254
Ali, znam sta je politika.
To je moj par rukava.

1317
01:05:30,288 --> 01:05:31,915
Ja sa vam omogucio izbore
zar ne?

1318
01:05:31,957 --> 01:05:34,084
I ucinicu, da vas
ponovo izaberu.

1319
01:05:34,126 --> 01:05:37,926
Cenim sve sto ste ucinili
za mene.

1320
01:05:37,963 --> 01:05:39,726
Zato, skinite se sa slucaja.

1321
01:05:39,764 --> 01:05:41,254
Ali, zasto?

1322
01:05:41,299 --> 01:05:44,496
Zato sto ste Pontius Pilate
od prvog trenutka.

1323
01:05:44,536 --> 01:05:47,130
Ne verujem...

1324
01:05:47,172 --> 01:05:48,764
Ja sam posten covek...

1325
01:05:48,807 --> 01:05:50,775
i niko me nece
spreciti...

1326
01:05:50,809 --> 01:05:52,743
da cinim ono sto mislim
da je najbolje.

1327
01:05:53,678 --> 01:05:55,646
Bako!

1328
01:05:55,680 --> 01:05:56,942
Bako!

1329
01:05:56,982 --> 01:05:58,472
Bako!

1330
01:05:58,517 --> 01:06:00,007
Laku noc, Terry.

1331
01:06:00,051 --> 01:06:01,518
Laku noc, Alice.

1332
01:06:01,553 --> 01:06:03,020
Pravo u krevet.

1333
01:06:03,054 --> 01:06:05,488
Obecala sam vasoj majci
da cete biti u krevetu u 8:00...

1334
01:06:05,524 --> 01:06:06,650
a to je proslo.

1335
01:06:06,691 --> 01:06:08,488
Zar ne ides i ti?

1336
01:06:08,527 --> 01:06:11,121
Dolazim brzo da vas
ususkam. A sad, tutanj!

1337
01:06:11,163 --> 01:06:15,623
Moze li veliki poljubac
za deku, hmm?

1338
01:06:17,769 --> 01:06:18,895
Hmmph!

1339
01:06:18,937 --> 01:06:20,097
Hmmph!

1340
01:06:21,106 --> 01:06:23,574
Bas lepo ponasanje!

1341
01:06:23,608 --> 01:06:25,235
Bez zagrljaja, bez poljubca,
nista.

1342
01:06:25,277 --> 01:06:26,744
Ne krivim ih.

1343
01:06:26,778 --> 01:06:29,338
Covek koji je strpao Deda Mraza 
u ludnicu.

1344
01:06:30,649 --> 01:06:32,480
Vidis na sta mislim?

1345
01:06:37,822 --> 01:06:39,449
Hej.

1346
01:06:55,207 --> 01:06:56,367
Ne brini za mene.

1347
01:06:56,408 --> 01:06:58,239
Imam najboljeg advokata
na svetu.

1348
01:06:58,276 --> 01:07:00,039
Koliko ce sve ovo
trajati?

1349
01:07:00,078 --> 01:07:01,272
Mozda nedelju dana.

1350
01:07:01,313 --> 01:07:03,042
Nedelju?! Cini se, nemoguce!

1351
01:07:03,081 --> 01:07:05,049
Taj advokat nece biti 
toliko glup...

1352
01:07:05,083 --> 01:07:07,677
da mu dozvoli da bilo sta prizna.
Sve ce poricati.

1353
01:07:07,719 --> 01:07:09,778
Dovescu svedoke,
i on ce.

1354
01:07:10,989 --> 01:07:12,684
Slusajte...

1355
01:07:12,724 --> 01:07:14,692
Svim prisutnima, koji imaju
posla

1356
01:07:14,726 --> 01:07:19,186
u Vrhovnom sudu
drzave New York...

1357
01:07:19,231 --> 01:07:21,927
pridjite, predstavite,
da vas cujemo.

1358
01:07:24,402 --> 01:07:27,860
Imate Kris Kringle'-ove
potpisane papire.

1359
01:07:27,906 --> 01:07:31,364
Zelim da pozovem prvog 
svedoka.

1360
01:07:31,409 --> 01:07:34,901
Mr. Kringle,
pridjite

1361
01:07:46,791 --> 01:07:48,258
Dobro jutro, Vasa Visosti.

1362
01:07:48,293 --> 01:07:50,284
Zaklinjete li se

1363
01:07:50,328 --> 01:07:54,230
da ce vase svedocenje, biti
istina...

1364
01:07:54,266 --> 01:07:56,234
u ime Boga?

1365
01:07:56,268 --> 01:07:57,462
Zaklinjem se.

1366
01:07:57,502 --> 01:08:00,562
Pre nego sto pocnete, zelim 
da pojasnim svedoku...

1367
01:08:00,605 --> 01:08:02,300
ovo je saslusanje,
ne sudjenje.

1368
01:08:02,340 --> 01:08:03,864
Gospodine Kringle...

1369
01:08:03,908 --> 01:08:06,274
Ne morate da odgovarate, ukoliko
ne zelite...

1370
01:08:06,311 --> 01:08:08,939
Ili da govorite, uopste.

1371
01:08:08,980 --> 01:08:10,743
Nemamo prigovora,
Vasa Visosti.

1372
01:08:12,484 --> 01:08:14,884
Bice mi draga da odgovorim
na sva pitanja, ako je moguce.

1373
01:08:16,921 --> 01:08:18,912
Koje je vase ime?

1374
01:08:18,957 --> 01:08:20,117
Kris Kringle.

1375
01:08:21,760 --> 01:08:23,227
Gde zivite?

1376
01:08:23,261 --> 01:08:25,729
To ce ishod ovog
saslusanja odluciti.

1377
01:08:31,369 --> 01:08:33,929
Zanimljiv odgovor,
gospodine Kringle.

1378
01:08:35,774 --> 01:08:37,935
Da li verujete da ste 
Deda Mraz?

1379
01:08:37,976 --> 01:08:39,637
Naravno.

1380
01:08:44,983 --> 01:08:47,474
Drzava se povlaci, 
Vasa Visosti.

1381
01:08:55,226 --> 01:08:56,693
Gospodine Gailey...

1382
01:08:56,728 --> 01:08:59,196
da li zelite da ispitate
svedoka?

1383
01:08:59,230 --> 01:09:01,391
Verujem da je bio zaposlen
kao Deda Mraz.

1384
01:09:01,433 --> 01:09:04,027
Mozda nije dobro razumeo
pitanje.

1385
01:09:04,069 --> 01:09:06,663
Oh, savrseno sam razumeo,
Vasa Visosti

1386
01:09:10,942 --> 01:09:13,410
Nemam pitanja, 
za sada.

1387
01:09:16,915 --> 01:09:18,507
Hvala.

1388
01:09:21,920 --> 01:09:23,581
U skladu sa ovom
izjavom...

1389
01:09:23,621 --> 01:09:26,556
da li odbrana zeli nesto da kaze?

1390
01:09:26,591 --> 01:09:28,559
Zelim, Vasa Visosti.

1391
01:09:28,593 --> 01:09:31,892
Potpuno sam svestan misljenja 
mog klijenta.

1392
01:09:31,930 --> 01:09:33,261
To je ceo slucaj, protiv njega.

1393
01:09:33,298 --> 01:09:36,790
svi ti komplikovani testovi
doveli su do ovde:

1394
01:09:36,835 --> 01:09:39,030
Gospodin Kringle 
nije uracunljiv...

1395
01:09:39,070 --> 01:09:40,867
zato sto veruje da je
Deda Mraz.

1396
01:09:40,905 --> 01:09:42,236
I to je logicna...

1397
01:09:42,273 --> 01:09:44,867
i razumna pretpostavka...

1398
01:09:44,909 --> 01:09:48,242
Ali, ne bi bilo tako, da, gosp. Klerk
Gosp. Marrah, ili ja...

1399
01:09:48,279 --> 01:09:49,837
verujemo da smo
Deda Mraz.

1400
01:09:49,881 --> 01:09:52,543
Svako ko misli da je
Deda Mraz nije uracunljiv.

1401
01:09:52,584 --> 01:09:54,142
Nije neophodno.

1402
01:09:54,185 --> 01:09:56,653
Vi verujete da ste 
sudija Harper...

1403
01:09:56,688 --> 01:09:59,953
niko ne spori vas razum
zato sto vi jeste Harper.

1404
01:09:59,991 --> 01:10:02,687
Znam to i sam,
mladicu.

1405
01:10:02,727 --> 01:10:04,524
Gospodin Kringle je tema
ovog saslusanja.

1406
01:10:04,562 --> 01:10:05,722
Da, Vasa Visosti...

1407
01:10:05,764 --> 01:10:08,699
i ako on kao osoba veruje
da je neko...

1408
01:10:08,733 --> 01:10:11,827
bas kao i vi, onda 
je i on, takodje razuman.

1409
01:10:11,870 --> 01:10:13,030
Cinjenica, ali on to nije.

1410
01:10:13,071 --> 01:10:14,197
Oh, ali jeste.

1411
01:10:14,239 --> 01:10:15,907
Jeste sta?

1412
01:10:16,040 --> 01:10:19,009
Nameravam da dokazem
da je g. Kringle Deda Mraz.

1413
01:10:20,745 --> 01:10:22,872
I on je lud!

1414
01:10:35,326 --> 01:10:37,760
Zdravo draga...
Zao mi je sto kasnim...

1415
01:10:37,795 --> 01:10:40,628
Uzmi kaput. Rezervisao sam 
nas sto kod Luigi-ja.

1416
01:10:40,665 --> 01:10:41,791
Idemo da proslavimo!

1417
01:10:41,832 --> 01:10:43,265
Sta slavimo?

1418
01:10:43,301 --> 01:10:45,769
Procitej sve o tome. "Gailey 
je ubacio bombu u sudnicu."

1419
01:10:45,803 --> 01:10:47,771
Da, procitala sam to.

1420
01:10:47,805 --> 01:10:50,774
Nisam video ovo...
Prva strana! Odlicno!

1421
01:10:50,808 --> 01:10:52,742
Nisi valjda siguran u vezi sa tim?

1422
01:10:52,777 --> 01:10:54,244
Naravno da jesam.

1423
01:10:54,278 --> 01:10:56,746
Ali ne mozes dokazati
da je on Deda Mraz.

1424
01:10:56,781 --> 01:10:59,306
Zasto ne? Videla si kako se
Macy i Gimbel rukuju.

1425
01:10:59,350 --> 01:11:01,818
I to je bilo nemoguce,
ali, dogodilo se.

1426
01:11:01,852 --> 01:11:03,285
To je najbolja odbrana koju
mogu da upotrebim.

1427
01:11:03,321 --> 01:11:05,789
Popuno logicno i
savrseno neocekivano.

1428
01:11:05,823 --> 01:11:07,313
I popuno suludo.

1429
01:11:07,358 --> 01:11:08,825
A tvoji sefovi...

1430
01:11:08,859 --> 01:11:10,588
Haislip i Mackenzie
i ostali?

1431
01:11:10,628 --> 01:11:11,754
Sta oni kazu?

1432
01:11:11,796 --> 01:11:13,764
Da ugrozavam prestiz
i dostojanstvo...

1433
01:11:13,798 --> 01:11:15,766
stare, cenjene
advokatske firme...

1434
01:11:15,800 --> 01:11:18,268
i da, ili odmah bacim
ovaj slucaj...

1435
01:11:18,302 --> 01:11:19,769
ili ce oni
izbaciti mene.

1436
01:11:19,804 --> 01:11:21,328
Ipak sam ih pobedio. 
Dao sam otkaz.

1437
01:11:21,372 --> 01:11:22,839
Frede, nisi valja.

1438
01:11:22,873 --> 01:11:25,034
Naravno da jesam.
Necu da izneverim Krisa.

1439
01:11:25,076 --> 01:11:27,840
Potreban sam mu,
a on, svima nama.

1440
01:11:27,878 --> 01:11:29,641
Dragi,
on je divan stari covek...

1441
01:11:29,680 --> 01:11:33,582
I ja ti se divim, sto zelis da
mu pomognes...

1442
01:11:33,617 --> 01:11:36,085
Ali, moras biti razuman
i suociti se sa cinjenicama.

1443
01:11:36,120 --> 01:11:38,088
Ne mozes tek tako 
upropastiti karijeru...

1444
01:11:38,122 --> 01:11:39,783
Zbog sentimentalnosti.

1445
01:11:39,824 --> 01:11:41,792
Ali ja se ne odricem 
svoje karijere.

1446
01:11:41,826 --> 01:11:43,794
Ako Haislip 
tako misli...

1447
01:11:43,828 --> 01:11:45,796
Mislice i u drugim firmama.

1448
01:11:45,830 --> 01:11:48,298
Siguran sam da hoce.
Otvoricu svoju.

1449
01:11:48,332 --> 01:11:50,800
Kakve ces slucajeve dobijati?

1450
01:11:50,835 --> 01:11:53,804
Verovatno ljude koji su
prepusteni sebi, kao Kris.

1451
01:11:53,838 --> 01:11:55,806
Uostalom, to je jedino
zabavno u pravu..

1452
01:11:55,840 --> 01:11:58,741
Ako verujes u mene...

1453
01:11:58,776 --> 01:12:00,573
sve ce...

1454
01:12:02,079 --> 01:12:05,242
Ti ne verujes u mene,
zar ne?

1455
01:12:05,282 --> 01:12:08,945
Ne radi se o verovanju.
Vec o zdravom razumu.

1456
01:12:10,788 --> 01:12:12,915
Vera je kada si ubedjen u stvari...

1457
01:12:12,957 --> 01:12:15,755
i kada ti zdrav razum,
to ne dozvoljava.

1458
01:12:15,793 --> 01:12:18,353
Nije samo Kris,
tako je i u parnicama.

1459
01:12:18,396 --> 01:12:19,920
Stoji iza svega u
sta veruje.

1460
01:12:19,964 --> 01:12:21,989
To je ljubaznost, radost, ljubav,
i ostale neopipljive stvari.

1461
01:12:22,033 --> 01:12:23,864
Fred,
govoris kao dete.

1462
01:12:23,901 --> 01:12:25,391
Zivis u realnom svetu!

1463
01:12:25,436 --> 01:12:26,903
Te slatke neopipljive
stvari, ne vrede mnogo.

1464
01:12:26,937 --> 01:12:28,427
Neces tako daleko 
dogurati.

1465
01:12:28,472 --> 01:12:31,270
Zavisi sta pod tom
podrazumevas.

1466
01:12:31,308 --> 01:12:33,276
Ocigledno, imamo
razlicite definicije.

1467
01:12:33,310 --> 01:12:35,778
Pricali smo o divnim
planovima.

1468
01:12:35,813 --> 01:12:37,940
A onda si postao idealista.

1469
01:12:37,982 --> 01:12:40,780
Dao si otkaz, odbacio
sigurnost,

1470
01:12:40,818 --> 01:12:43,946
I ocekujes da budem
srecna zbog toga!

1471
01:12:43,988 --> 01:12:47,287
Da. Ocigledno sam
previse ocekivao.

1472
01:12:47,324 --> 01:12:49,451
Jednog dana ces,
shvatiti...

1473
01:12:49,493 --> 01:12:51,290
da tvoj nacin suocavanja
sa realnim svetom...

1474
01:12:51,328 --> 01:12:52,795
jednostavno, ne funkcionise.

1475
01:12:52,830 --> 01:12:54,229
A kada se to dogodi...

1476
01:12:54,265 --> 01:12:56,062
nemoj da zaboravis te
slatke neopipljive stvari.

1477
01:12:56,100 --> 01:12:57,897
Otkrices, da su to
jedine stvari...

1478
01:12:57,935 --> 01:12:59,266
vredne zivljenja.

1479
01:13:07,778 --> 01:13:10,338
Ovi reporteri su od mene
napravili sadisticko cudoviste...

1480
01:13:10,381 --> 01:13:11,848
koje voli da davi macke...

1481
01:13:11,882 --> 01:13:13,747
i kida krila leptirima.

1482
01:13:13,784 --> 01:13:14,910
Zasto ovaj stari covek...

1483
01:13:14,952 --> 01:13:18,410
Tommy, donesi mi
makaze, hoces li?

1484
01:13:18,456 --> 01:13:20,424
Pogledaj u spavacoj
sobi.

1485
01:13:20,458 --> 01:13:22,449
Tako je, dobri decko.

1486
01:13:23,894 --> 01:13:26,362
Nezelim da pricas o
slucaju pred njim.

1487
01:13:26,397 --> 01:13:28,262
Slomice mu srce.

1488
01:13:28,299 --> 01:13:30,267
I kada smo ve ckod teme,
slazem se sa njima.

1489
01:13:30,301 --> 01:13:32,269
Gospodin Kringle izgleda kao fini, 
stari covek.

1490
01:13:32,303 --> 01:13:34,771
Ne vidim zasto ga i dalje
gonis.

1491
01:13:34,805 --> 01:13:36,773
Prvo,
ja ga ne gonim.

1492
01:13:36,807 --> 01:13:38,274
Ja ga tuzim.

1493
01:13:38,309 --> 01:13:40,937
I drugo,
i meni se dopada starac.

1494
01:13:40,978 --> 01:13:43,276
Voleo bih da se nisam
upleo u ovo.

1495
01:13:43,314 --> 01:13:45,782
Ali, sada je kasno. I ne mogu
nista da ucinim.

1496
01:13:45,816 --> 01:13:47,784
Sve je na drzavi
New York.

1497
01:13:47,818 --> 01:13:49,285
Ja sam samo njen legalni
predstavnik.

1498
01:13:49,320 --> 01:13:51,288
Kringle je obelezen kao opasnost
po drustvo...

1499
01:13:51,322 --> 01:13:52,949
Od strane kompetentnih
doktora.

1500
01:13:52,990 --> 01:13:55,220
Moja je duznost da
stitim interese drzave...

1501
01:13:55,259 --> 01:13:56,886
I sagledam u cemu je njegova
greska.

1502
01:13:56,927 --> 01:13:58,827
Bez obzira sta 
govorili o meni...

1503
01:13:58,863 --> 01:14:00,387
Ja to moram.

1504
01:14:00,431 --> 01:14:03,730
Ponekad pozelim da sam se
udala za mesara ili 

1505
01:14:03,767 --> 01:14:06,395
Vodoinstalatera.
Pa, draga, ako izgubim slucaj...

1506
01:14:06,437 --> 01:14:08,769
Mozda ti se zelja ispuni.

1507
01:14:20,784 --> 01:14:22,183
Zdravo, Kris.

1508
01:14:34,131 --> 01:14:35,598
Vase ime?

1509
01:14:35,633 --> 01:14:37,032
R.H. Macy.

1510
01:14:37,067 --> 01:14:38,193
Vi ste vlasnik...

1511
01:14:38,235 --> 01:14:39,702
Jedne od najvecih
robnih kuca...

1512
01:14:39,737 --> 01:14:40,965
u New York City-ju?

1513
01:14:41,005 --> 01:14:42,131
Najvece.

1514
01:14:42,173 --> 01:14:45,574
Ko je gospodin koji 
sedi tamo?

1515
01:14:45,609 --> 01:14:46,803
Kris Kringle.

1516
01:14:46,844 --> 01:14:48,277
- Vas zaposleni?
- Da.

1517
01:14:48,312 --> 01:14:49,939
Verujete li da je
iskren?

1518
01:14:49,980 --> 01:14:51,106
Da.

1519
01:14:51,148 --> 01:14:53,284
Verujete li da zna
sta govori?

1520
01:14:53,319 --> 01:14:54,376
Naravno.

1521
01:14:54,418 --> 01:14:56,215
Gospodine Macy, 
vi ste pod zakletvom.

1522
01:14:56,253 --> 01:14:58,414
Zaista verujete da je
on Deda Mraz?

1523
01:14:58,455 --> 01:15:00,753
Pa, ja...

1524
01:15:05,429 --> 01:15:07,989
Pa, odaje takav utisak...

1525
01:15:08,032 --> 01:15:11,433
Da li zaista verujete da je
on Deda Mraz?

1526
01:15:19,777 --> 01:15:21,267
Verujem.

1527
01:15:21,312 --> 01:15:22,438
Zaista?

1528
01:15:22,479 --> 01:15:23,969
To je sve.

1529
01:15:36,627 --> 01:15:38,322
Psiholog!

1530
01:15:38,362 --> 01:15:41,456
Gde si diplomirao,
u dopisnoj skoli?

1531
01:15:42,466 --> 01:15:43,956
Otpusten si.

1532
01:15:45,736 --> 01:15:47,761
Vasa Visosti, prigovaram 
na ovo svedocenje.

1533
01:15:47,805 --> 01:15:49,773
To je suludo, beznacajno,
i bespredmetno.

1534
01:15:49,807 --> 01:15:51,934
Gospodin Gailey pravi cirkus
od sudnice.

1535
01:15:51,976 --> 01:15:53,705
Deda Mraz ne postoji...

1536
01:15:53,744 --> 01:15:55,211
I svi to znaju.

1537
01:15:55,246 --> 01:15:57,714
Priznajem da je to
stvar misljenja.

1538
01:15:57,748 --> 01:16:00,114
Moze li gospodin Marrah dokazati 
da Deda Mraz ne postoji?

1539
01:16:00,150 --> 01:16:01,879
Ne. I nemam nameru.

1540
01:16:01,919 --> 01:16:04,353
Ovo je drzavni vrhovni sud...

1541
01:16:04,388 --> 01:16:06,879
Cije vreme ne zelim da trosim
na gluposti!

1542
01:16:06,924 --> 01:16:08,892
Gospodin Marrah je umislio
da je sudija.

1543
01:16:08,926 --> 01:16:11,895
On zeli da odlucuje koje
svedocenje cu predstaviti.

1544
01:16:11,929 --> 01:16:14,727
Zahtevamo hitnu odluku suda.

1545
01:16:14,765 --> 01:16:17,290
Da li, ili ne postoji
Deda Mraz?

1546
01:16:19,436 --> 01:16:20,903
Pa...

1547
01:16:20,938 --> 01:16:22,735
Hmmm!

1548
01:16:28,445 --> 01:16:31,846
Sud ce razmotriti zahtev.

1549
01:16:34,785 --> 01:16:37,754
Ne zanima me sta radite...

1550
01:16:37,788 --> 01:16:40,256
Ali, ako odlucite
da Deda Mraz ne postoji...

1551
01:16:40,291 --> 01:16:42,759
Bolje potrazite neku farmu
sa pilicima.

1552
01:16:42,793 --> 01:16:46,251
Jer necete moci da radite
ni u jednom sudu.

1553
01:16:46,297 --> 01:16:48,288
Ali, Charley, saslusaj...

1554
01:16:48,332 --> 01:16:50,300
Ja sam odgovoran sudija.

1555
01:16:50,334 --> 01:16:52,302
Ja sam pod zakletvom.

1556
01:16:52,336 --> 01:16:55,328
Kako mogu ozbiljno da odlucim 
da Deda Mraz postoji?

1557
01:16:55,372 --> 01:16:57,363
Zasto ne mozes...

1558
01:16:58,876 --> 01:17:00,343
U redu.

1559
01:17:00,377 --> 01:17:03,835
reci im da je Drzavni sud
odlucio...

1560
01:17:03,881 --> 01:17:05,348
Da Deda Mraz ne postoji.

1561
01:17:05,382 --> 01:17:06,610
Bice u svim novinama.

1562
01:17:06,650 --> 01:17:08,845
Deca nece vise kaciti
svoje carape.

1563
01:17:08,886 --> 01:17:11,184
I sta ce se dogoditi
sa svim igrackama...

1564
01:17:11,221 --> 01:17:13,348
koje bi trebalo da budu
u tim carapama?

1565
01:17:13,390 --> 01:17:14,857
Niko ih nece kupiti.

1566
01:17:14,892 --> 01:17:17,360
Nestace proizvodnje igracaka.

1567
01:17:17,394 --> 01:17:20,557
Morace da otpuste
veliki broj radnika...

1568
01:17:20,597 --> 01:17:22,565
Unija zaposlenih.

1569
01:17:22,599 --> 01:17:26,228
Imaces C.I.O. i A.F.L. 
za protivnike.

1570
01:17:26,270 --> 01:17:28,740
I obozavace te
zbog toga.

1571
01:17:28,873 --> 01:17:31,967
To ce i javno iskazati,
svojim glasovima.

1572
01:17:32,009 --> 01:17:34,910
I ljudi iz prodavnica i
robnih kuca ce te voleti...

1573
01:17:34,946 --> 01:17:37,574
I ovi, sto prave Bozicne cestitke...

1574
01:17:37,615 --> 01:17:39,082
I fabrike slatkisa.

1575
01:17:39,117 --> 01:17:43,918
Oh, Henry, bices nevidjeno 
popularan momak.

1576
01:17:43,955 --> 01:17:46,321
A Armija Spasa?

1577
01:17:46,357 --> 01:17:48,848
Zasto, oni imaju Deda Mrazove
na svakom cosku...

1578
01:17:48,893 --> 01:17:50,554
Ali,

1579
01:17:50,595 --> 01:17:51,926
Samo ti nastavi, Henry.

1580
01:17:51,963 --> 01:17:54,193
Uradi kako mislis da treba.

1581
01:17:54,232 --> 01:17:56,700
Vrati se tamo i
kazi im...

1582
01:17:56,734 --> 01:17:59,794
Da si odlucio da
Deda Mraz ne postoji.

1583
01:18:00,805 --> 01:18:03,205
Ako to uradis, zapamti:

1584
01:18:03,241 --> 01:18:05,072
Mozes da racunas samo
na dva glasa...

1585
01:18:05,109 --> 01:18:07,873
Sopstveni i onog 
 tuzioca.

1586
01:18:10,414 --> 01:18:12,609
Tuzilac je
republikanac.

1587
01:18:13,818 --> 01:18:14,978
Ustanite!

1588
01:18:31,936 --> 01:18:33,904
Pre nego sto donesem
odluku...

1589
01:18:33,938 --> 01:18:38,034
ovaj sud je konsultovao
najvece moguce autoritete.

1590
01:18:40,178 --> 01:18:42,237
Pitanje Deda Mraza...

1591
01:18:42,280 --> 01:18:44,510
Cini se da je mnogo vece
od misljenja.

1592
