1842
01:33:37,440 --> 01:33:40,102
Hvala, Kris.
Srecan Bozic.

1843
01:33:40,143 --> 01:33:41,371
Srecan Bozic
i vama.

1844
01:33:41,411 --> 01:33:44,244
I vama, moja draga,
i jos mnogo njih.

1845
01:33:44,280 --> 01:33:46,271
Dovidjenja draga.

1846
01:33:46,316 --> 01:33:48,250
Dovidjenja gospodjo Walker.

1847
01:33:48,284 --> 01:33:49,751
Dovidjenja, Alfred.

1848
01:33:49,786 --> 01:33:51,276
Dovidjenja , Suzie.

1849
01:33:54,824 --> 01:33:57,691
Mora da je ovo skretanje.

1850
01:33:57,727 --> 01:33:59,695
Tako je. Ashley.

1851
01:33:59,729 --> 01:34:02,721
Sada pravo
jos cetiri bloka.

1852
01:34:04,000 --> 01:34:07,834
Verujem. Verujem.

1853
01:34:11,307 --> 01:34:13,639
Stani, Cika Fred! Stani!

1854
01:34:13,676 --> 01:34:15,644
Stani! Stani!

1855
01:34:19,315 --> 01:34:20,509
Suzie!

1856
01:34:21,518 --> 01:34:22,712
Suzie!

1857
01:34:24,854 --> 01:34:26,481
Suzie, kuda si krenula?

1858
01:34:26,523 --> 01:34:28,047
Sta se dogadja?

1859
01:34:28,091 --> 01:34:30,116
- Suzie!
- Suzie!

1860
01:34:32,362 --> 01:34:34,762
Suzie, gde si?

1861
01:34:34,798 --> 01:34:36,265
Gore sam!

1862
01:34:36,299 --> 01:34:38,267
Ne bi trebalo da trcis
u tudjoj kuci.

1863
01:34:38,301 --> 01:34:39,768
Znas ti i bolje od toga.

1864
01:34:39,803 --> 01:34:43,830
